2574// Radix sorts tdefl_sym_freq[] array by 16-bit key m_key. Returns ptr to sorted
2575// values.
2576typedef struct {
2577 mz_uint16 m_key, m_sym_index;
2578} tdefl_sym_freq;
2579static tdefl_sym_freq *tdefl_radix_sort_syms(mz_uint num_syms,
2580 tdefl_sym_freq *pSyms0,
2581 tdefl_sym_freq *pSyms1) {
2582 mz_uint32 total_passes = 2, pass_shift, pass, i, hist[256 * 2];
2583 tdefl_sym_freq *pCur_syms = pSyms0, *pNew_syms = pSyms1;
2584 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(hist);
2585 for (i = 0; i < num_syms; i++) {
2586 mz_uint freq = pSyms0[i].m_key;
2587 hist[freq & 0xFF]++;
2588 hist[256 + ((freq >> 8) & 0xFF)]++;
2589 }
2590 while ((total_passes > 1) && (num_syms == hist[(total_passes - 1) * 256]))
2591 total_passes--;
2592 for (pass_shift = 0, pass = 0; pass < total_passes; pass++, pass_shift += 8) {
2593 const mz_uint32 *pHist = &hist[pass << 8];
2594 mz_uint offsets[256], cur_ofs = 0;
2595 for (i = 0; i < 256; i++) {
2596 offsets[i] = cur_ofs;
2597 cur_ofs += pHist[i];
2598 }
2599 for (i = 0; i < num_syms; i++)
2600 pNew_syms[offsets[(pCur_syms[i].m_key >> pass_shift) & 0xFF]++] =
2601 pCur_syms[i];
2602 {
2603 tdefl_sym_freq *t = pCur_syms;
2604 pCur_syms = pNew_syms;
2605 pNew_syms = t;
2606 }
2607 }
2608 return pCur_syms;
2609}
2610
2611// tdefl_calculate_minimum_redundancy() originally written by: Alistair Moffat,
2612// alistair@cs.mu.oz.au, Jyrki Katajainen, jyrki@diku.dk, November 1996.
2613static void tdefl_calculate_minimum_redundancy(tdefl_sym_freq *A, int n) {
2614 int root, leaf, next, avbl, used, dpth;
2615 if (n == 0)
2616 return;
2617 else if (n == 1) {
2618 A[0].m_key = 1;
2619 return;
2620 }
2621 A[0].m_key += A[1].m_key;
2622 root = 0;
2623 leaf = 2;
2624 for (next = 1; next < n - 1; next++) {
2625 if (leaf >= n || A[root].m_key < A[leaf].m_key) {
2626 A[next].m_key = A[root].m_key;
2627 A[root++].m_key = (mz_uint16)next;
2628 } else
2629 A[next].m_key = A[leaf++].m_key;
2630 if (leaf >= n || (root < next && A[root].m_key < A[leaf].m_key)) {
2631 A[next].m_key = (mz_uint16)(A[next].m_key + A[root].m_key);
2632 A[root++].m_key = (mz_uint16)next;
2633 } else
2634 A[next].m_key = (mz_uint16)(A[next].m_key + A[leaf++].m_key);
2635 }
2636 A[n - 2].m_key = 0;
2637 for (next = n - 3; next >= 0; next--)
2638 A[next].m_key = A[A[next].m_key].m_key + 1;
2639 avbl = 1;
2640 used = dpth = 0;
2641 root = n - 2;
2642 next = n - 1;
2643 while (avbl > 0) {
2644 while (root >= 0 && (int)A[root].m_key == dpth) {
2645 used++;
2646 root--;
2647 }
2648 while (avbl > used) {
2649 A[next--].m_key = (mz_uint16)(dpth);
2650 avbl--;
2651 }
2652 avbl = 2 * used;
2653 dpth++;
2654 used = 0;
2655 }
2656}
2657
2658// Limits canonical Huffman code table's max code size.
2659enum { TDEFL_MAX_SUPPORTED_HUFF_CODESIZE = 32 };
2660static void tdefl_huffman_enforce_max_code_size(int *pNum_codes,
2661 int code_list_len,
2662 int max_code_size) {
2663 int i;
2664 mz_uint32 total = 0;
2665 if (code_list_len <= 1)
2666 return;
2667 for (i = max_code_size + 1; i <= TDEFL_MAX_SUPPORTED_HUFF_CODESIZE; i++)
2668 pNum_codes[max_code_size] += pNum_codes[i];
2669 for (i = max_code_size; i > 0; i--)
2670 total += (((mz_uint32)pNum_codes[i]) << (max_code_size - i));
2671 while (total != (1UL << max_code_size)) {
2672 pNum_codes[max_code_size]--;
2673 for (i = max_code_size - 1; i > 0; i--)
2674 if (pNum_codes[i]) {
2675 pNum_codes[i]--;
2676 pNum_codes[i + 1] += 2;
2677 break;
2678 }
2679 total--;
2680 }
2681}
2682
2683static void tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(tdefl_compressor *d, int table_num,
2684 int table_len, int code_size_limit,
2685 int static_table) {
2686 int i, j, l, num_codes[1 + TDEFL_MAX_SUPPORTED_HUFF_CODESIZE];
2687 mz_uint next_code[TDEFL_MAX_SUPPORTED_HUFF_CODESIZE + 1];
2688 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(num_codes);
2689 if (static_table) {
2690 for (i = 0; i < table_len; i++)
2691 num_codes[d->m_huff_code_sizes[table_num][i]]++;
2692 } else {
2693 tdefl_sym_freq syms0[TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS], syms1[TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS],
2694 *pSyms;
2695 int num_used_syms = 0;
2696 const mz_uint16 *pSym_count = &d->m_huff_count[table_num][0];
2697 for (i = 0; i < table_len; i++)
2698 if (pSym_count[i]) {
2699 syms0[num_used_syms].m_key = (mz_uint16)pSym_count[i];
2700 syms0[num_used_syms++].m_sym_index = (mz_uint16)i;
2701 }
2702
2703 pSyms = tdefl_radix_sort_syms(num_used_syms, syms0, syms1);
2704 tdefl_calculate_minimum_redundancy(pSyms, num_used_syms);
2705
2706 for (i = 0; i < num_used_syms; i++)
2707 num_codes[pSyms[i].m_key]++;
2708
2709 tdefl_huffman_enforce_max_code_size(num_codes, num_used_syms,
2710 code_size_limit);
2711
2712 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(d->m_huff_code_sizes[table_num]);
2713 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(d->m_huff_codes[table_num]);
2714 for (i = 1, j = num_used_syms; i <= code_size_limit; i++)
2715 for (l = num_codes[i]; l > 0; l--)
2716 d->m_huff_code_sizes[table_num][pSyms[--j].m_sym_index] = (mz_uint8)(i);
2717 }
2718
2719 next_code[1] = 0;
2720 for (j = 0, i = 2; i <= code_size_limit; i++)
2721 next_code[i] = j = ((j + num_codes[i - 1]) << 1);
2722
2723 for (i = 0; i < table_len; i++) {
2724 mz_uint rev_code = 0, code, code_size;
2725 if ((code_size = d->m_huff_code_sizes[table_num][i]) == 0)
2726 continue;
2727 code = next_code[code_size]++;
2728 for (l = code_size; l > 0; l--, code >>= 1)
2729 rev_code = (rev_code << 1) | (code & 1);
2730 d->m_huff_codes[table_num][i] = (mz_uint16)rev_code;
2731 }
2732}
2733
2734#define TDEFL_PUT_BITS(b, l) \
2735 do { \
2736 mz_uint bits = b; \
2737 mz_uint len = l; \
2738 MZ_ASSERT(bits <= ((1U << len) - 1U)); \
2739 d->m_bit_buffer |= (bits << d->m_bits_in); \
2740 d->m_bits_in += len; \
2741 while (d->m_bits_in >= 8) { \
2742 if (d->m_pOutput_buf < d->m_pOutput_buf_end) \
2743 *d->m_pOutput_buf++ = (mz_uint8)(d->m_bit_buffer); \
2744 d->m_bit_buffer >>= 8; \
2745 d->m_bits_in -= 8; \
2746 } \
2747 } \
2748 MZ_MACRO_END
2749
2750#define TDEFL_RLE_PREV_CODE_SIZE() \
2751 { \
2752 if (rle_repeat_count) { \
2753 if (rle_repeat_count < 3) { \
2754 d->m_huff_count[2][prev_code_size] = (mz_uint16)( \
2755 d->m_huff_count[2][prev_code_size] + rle_repeat_count); \
2756 while (rle_repeat_count--) \
2757 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = prev_code_size; \
2758 } else { \
2759 d->m_huff_count[2][16] = (mz_uint16)(d->m_huff_count[2][16] + 1); \
2760 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = 16; \
2761 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = \
2762 (mz_uint8)(rle_repeat_count - 3); \
2763 } \
2764 rle_repeat_count = 0; \
2765 } \
2766 }
2767
2768#define TDEFL_RLE_ZERO_CODE_SIZE() \
2769 { \
2770 if (rle_z_count) { \
2771 if (rle_z_count < 3) { \
2772 d->m_huff_count[2][0] = \
2773 (mz_uint16)(d->m_huff_count[2][0] + rle_z_count); \
2774 while (rle_z_count--) \
2775 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = 0; \
2776 } else if (rle_z_count <= 10) { \
2777 d->m_huff_count[2][17] = (mz_uint16)(d->m_huff_count[2][17] + 1); \
2778 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = 17; \
2779 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = \
2780 (mz_uint8)(rle_z_count - 3); \
2781 } else { \
2782 d->m_huff_count[2][18] = (mz_uint16)(d->m_huff_count[2][18] + 1); \
2783 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = 18; \
2784 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = \
2785 (mz_uint8)(rle_z_count - 11); \
2786 } \
2787 rle_z_count = 0; \
2788 } \
2789 }
2790
2791static mz_uint8 s_tdefl_packed_code_size_syms_swizzle[] = {
2792 16, 17, 18, 0, 8, 7, 9, 6, 10, 5, 11, 4, 12, 3, 13, 2, 14, 1, 15};
2793
2794static void tdefl_start_dynamic_block(tdefl_compressor *d) {
2795 int num_lit_codes, num_dist_codes, num_bit_lengths;
2796 mz_uint i, total_code_sizes_to_pack, num_packed_code_sizes, rle_z_count,
2797 rle_repeat_count, packed_code_sizes_index;
2798 mz_uint8
2799 code_sizes_to_pack[TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_0 + TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_1],
2800 packed_code_sizes[TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_0 + TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_1],
2801 prev_code_size = 0xFF;
2802
2803 d->m_huff_count[0][256] = 1;
2804
2805 tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(d, 0, TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_0, 15, MZ_FALSE);
2806 tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(d, 1, TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_1, 15, MZ_FALSE);
2807
2808 for (num_lit_codes = 286; num_lit_codes > 257; num_lit_codes--)
2809 if (d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][num_lit_codes - 1])
2810 break;
2811 for (num_dist_codes = 30; num_dist_codes > 1; num_dist_codes--)
2812 if (d->m_huff_code_sizes[1][num_dist_codes - 1])
2813 break;
2814
2815 memcpy(code_sizes_to_pack, &d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][0],
2816 sizeof(mz_uint8) * num_lit_codes);
2817 memcpy(code_sizes_to_pack + num_lit_codes, &d->m_huff_code_sizes[1][0],
2818 sizeof(mz_uint8) * num_dist_codes);
2819 total_code_sizes_to_pack = num_lit_codes + num_dist_codes;
2820 num_packed_code_sizes = 0;
2821 rle_z_count = 0;
2822 rle_repeat_count = 0;
2823
2824 memset(&d->m_huff_count[2][0], 0,
2825 sizeof(d->m_huff_count[2][0]) * TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_2);
2826 for (i = 0; i < total_code_sizes_to_pack; i++) {
2827 mz_uint8 code_size = code_sizes_to_pack[i];
2828 if (!code_size) {
2829 TDEFL_RLE_PREV_CODE_SIZE();
2830 if (++rle_z_count == 138) {
2831 TDEFL_RLE_ZERO_CODE_SIZE();
2832 }
2833 } else {
2834 TDEFL_RLE_ZERO_CODE_SIZE();
2835 if (code_size != prev_code_size) {
2836 TDEFL_RLE_PREV_CODE_SIZE();
2837 d->m_huff_count[2][code_size] =
2838 (mz_uint16)(d->m_huff_count[2][code_size] + 1);
2839 packed_code_sizes[num_packed_code_sizes++] = code_size;
2840 } else if (++rle_repeat_count == 6) {
2841 TDEFL_RLE_PREV_CODE_SIZE();
2842 }
2843 }
2844 prev_code_size = code_size;
2845 }
2846 if (rle_repeat_count) {
2847 TDEFL_RLE_PREV_CODE_SIZE();
2848 } else {
2849 TDEFL_RLE_ZERO_CODE_SIZE();
2850 }
2851
2852 tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(d, 2, TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_2, 7, MZ_FALSE);
2853
2854 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(2, 2);
2855
2856 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(num_lit_codes - 257, 5);
2857 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(num_dist_codes - 1, 5);
2858
2859 for (num_bit_lengths = 18; num_bit_lengths >= 0; num_bit_lengths--)
2860 if (d->m_huff_code_sizes
2861 [2][s_tdefl_packed_code_size_syms_swizzle[num_bit_lengths]])
2862 break;
2863 num_bit_lengths = MZ_MAX(4, (num_bit_lengths + 1));
2864 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(num_bit_lengths - 4, 4);
2865 for (i = 0; (int)i < num_bit_lengths; i++)
2866 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(
2867 d->m_huff_code_sizes[2][s_tdefl_packed_code_size_syms_swizzle[i]], 3);
2868
2869 for (packed_code_sizes_index = 0;
2870 packed_code_sizes_index < num_packed_code_sizes;) {
2871 mz_uint code = packed_code_sizes[packed_code_sizes_index++];
2872 MZ_ASSERT(code < TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_2);
2873 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[2][code], d->m_huff_code_sizes[2][code]);
2874 if (code >= 16)
2875 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(packed_code_sizes[packed_code_sizes_index++],
2876 "\02\03\07"[code - 16]);
2877 }
2878}
2879
2880static void tdefl_start_static_block(tdefl_compressor *d) {
2881 mz_uint i;
2882 mz_uint8 *p = &d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][0];
2883
2884 for (i = 0; i <= 143; ++i)
2885 *p++ = 8;
2886 for (; i <= 255; ++i)
2887 *p++ = 9;
2888 for (; i <= 279; ++i)
2889 *p++ = 7;
2890 for (; i <= 287; ++i)
2891 *p++ = 8;
2892
2893 memset(d->m_huff_code_sizes[1], 5, 32);
2894
2895 tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(d, 0, 288, 15, MZ_TRUE);
2896 tdefl_optimize_huffman_table(d, 1, 32, 15, MZ_TRUE);
2897
2898 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(1, 2);
2899}
2900
2901static const mz_uint mz_bitmasks[17] = {
2902 0x0000, 0x0001, 0x0003, 0x0007, 0x000F, 0x001F, 0x003F, 0x007F, 0x00FF,
2903 0x01FF, 0x03FF, 0x07FF, 0x0FFF, 0x1FFF, 0x3FFF, 0x7FFF, 0xFFFF};
2904
2905#if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN && \
2906 MINIZ_HAS_64BIT_REGISTERS
2907static mz_bool tdefl_compress_lz_codes(tdefl_compressor *d) {
2908 mz_uint flags;
2909 mz_uint8 *pLZ_codes;
2910 mz_uint8 *pOutput_buf = d->m_pOutput_buf;
2911 mz_uint8 *pLZ_code_buf_end = d->m_pLZ_code_buf;
2912 mz_uint64 bit_buffer = d->m_bit_buffer;
2913 mz_uint bits_in = d->m_bits_in;
2914
2915#define TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(b, l) \
2916 { \
2917 bit_buffer |= (((mz_uint64)(b)) << bits_in); \
2918 bits_in += (l); \
2919 }
2920
2921 flags = 1;
2922 for (pLZ_codes = d->m_lz_code_buf; pLZ_codes < pLZ_code_buf_end;
2923 flags >>= 1) {
2924 if (flags == 1)
2925 flags = *pLZ_codes++ | 0x100;
2926
2927 if (flags & 1) {
2928 mz_uint s0, s1, n0, n1, sym, num_extra_bits;
2929 mz_uint match_len = pLZ_codes[0],
2930 match_dist = *(const mz_uint16 *)(pLZ_codes + 1);
2931 pLZ_codes += 3;
2932
2933 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]]);
2934 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(d->m_huff_codes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]],
2935 d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]]);
2936 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(match_len & mz_bitmasks[s_tdefl_len_extra[match_len]],
2937 s_tdefl_len_extra[match_len]);
2938
2939 // This sequence coaxes MSVC into using cmov's vs. jmp's.
2940 s0 = s_tdefl_small_dist_sym[match_dist & 511];
2941 n0 = s_tdefl_small_dist_extra[match_dist & 511];
2942 s1 = s_tdefl_large_dist_sym[match_dist >> 8];
2943 n1 = s_tdefl_large_dist_extra[match_dist >> 8];
2944 sym = (match_dist < 512) ? s0 : s1;
2945 num_extra_bits = (match_dist < 512) ? n0 : n1;
2946
2947 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[1][sym]);
2948 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(d->m_huff_codes[1][sym],
2949 d->m_huff_code_sizes[1][sym]);
2950 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(match_dist & mz_bitmasks[num_extra_bits],
2951 num_extra_bits);
2952 } else {
2953 mz_uint lit = *pLZ_codes++;
2954 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2955 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(d->m_huff_codes[0][lit],
2956 d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2957
2958 if (((flags & 2) == 0) && (pLZ_codes < pLZ_code_buf_end)) {
2959 flags >>= 1;
2960 lit = *pLZ_codes++;
2961 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2962 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(d->m_huff_codes[0][lit],
2963 d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2964
2965 if (((flags & 2) == 0) && (pLZ_codes < pLZ_code_buf_end)) {
2966 flags >>= 1;
2967 lit = *pLZ_codes++;
2968 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2969 TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST(d->m_huff_codes[0][lit],
2970 d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
2971 }
2972 }
2973 }
2974
2975 if (pOutput_buf >= d->m_pOutput_buf_end)
2976 return MZ_FALSE;
2977
2978 *(mz_uint64 *)pOutput_buf = bit_buffer;
2979 pOutput_buf += (bits_in >> 3);
2980 bit_buffer >>= (bits_in & ~7);
2981 bits_in &= 7;
2982 }
2983
2984#undef TDEFL_PUT_BITS_FAST
2985
2986 d->m_pOutput_buf = pOutput_buf;
2987 d->m_bits_in = 0;
2988 d->m_bit_buffer = 0;
2989
2990 while (bits_in) {
2991 mz_uint32 n = MZ_MIN(bits_in, 16);
2992 TDEFL_PUT_BITS((mz_uint)bit_buffer & mz_bitmasks[n], n);
2993 bit_buffer >>= n;
2994 bits_in -= n;
2995 }
2996
2997 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[0][256], d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][256]);
2998
2999 return (d->m_pOutput_buf < d->m_pOutput_buf_end);
3000}
3001#else
3002static mz_bool tdefl_compress_lz_codes(tdefl_compressor *d) {
3003 mz_uint flags;
3004 mz_uint8 *pLZ_codes;
3005
3006 flags = 1;
3007 for (pLZ_codes = d->m_lz_code_buf; pLZ_codes < d->m_pLZ_code_buf;
3008 flags >>= 1) {
3009 if (flags == 1)
3010 flags = *pLZ_codes++ | 0x100;
3011 if (flags & 1) {
3012 mz_uint sym, num_extra_bits;
3013 mz_uint match_len = pLZ_codes[0],
3014 match_dist = (pLZ_codes[1] | (pLZ_codes[2] << 8));
3015 pLZ_codes += 3;
3016
3017 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]]);
3018 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]],
3019 d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len]]);
3020 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(match_len & mz_bitmasks[s_tdefl_len_extra[match_len]],
3021 s_tdefl_len_extra[match_len]);
3022
3023 if (match_dist < 512) {
3024 sym = s_tdefl_small_dist_sym[match_dist];
3025 num_extra_bits = s_tdefl_small_dist_extra[match_dist];
3026 } else {
3027 sym = s_tdefl_large_dist_sym[match_dist >> 8];
3028 num_extra_bits = s_tdefl_large_dist_extra[match_dist >> 8];
3029 }
3030 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[1][sym], d->m_huff_code_sizes[1][sym]);
3031 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(match_dist & mz_bitmasks[num_extra_bits], num_extra_bits);
3032 } else {
3033 mz_uint lit = *pLZ_codes++;
3034 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
3035 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[0][lit], d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][lit]);
3036 }
3037 }
3038
3039 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_huff_codes[0][256], d->m_huff_code_sizes[0][256]);
3040
3041 return (d->m_pOutput_buf < d->m_pOutput_buf_end);
3042}
3043#endif // MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN &&
3044 // MINIZ_HAS_64BIT_REGISTERS
3045
3046static mz_bool tdefl_compress_block(tdefl_compressor *d, mz_bool static_block) {
3047 if (static_block)
3048 tdefl_start_static_block(d);
3049 else
3050 tdefl_start_dynamic_block(d);
3051 return tdefl_compress_lz_codes(d);
3052}
3053
3054static int tdefl_flush_block(tdefl_compressor *d, int flush) {
3055 mz_uint saved_bit_buf, saved_bits_in;
3056 mz_uint8 *pSaved_output_buf;
3057 mz_bool comp_block_succeeded = MZ_FALSE;
3058 int n, use_raw_block =
3059 ((d->m_flags & TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS) != 0) &&
3060 (d->m_lookahead_pos - d->m_lz_code_buf_dict_pos) <= d->m_dict_size;
3061 mz_uint8 *pOutput_buf_start =
3062 ((d->m_pPut_buf_func == NULL) &&
3063 ((*d->m_pOut_buf_size - d->m_out_buf_ofs) >= TDEFL_OUT_BUF_SIZE))
3064 ? ((mz_uint8 *)d->m_pOut_buf + d->m_out_buf_ofs)
3065 : d->m_output_buf;
3066
3067 d->m_pOutput_buf = pOutput_buf_start;
3068 d->m_pOutput_buf_end = d->m_pOutput_buf + TDEFL_OUT_BUF_SIZE - 16;
3069
3070 MZ_ASSERT(!d->m_output_flush_remaining);
3071 d->m_output_flush_ofs = 0;
3072 d->m_output_flush_remaining = 0;
3073
3074 *d->m_pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)(*d->m_pLZ_flags >> d->m_num_flags_left);
3075 d->m_pLZ_code_buf -= (d->m_num_flags_left == 8);
3076
3077 if ((d->m_flags & TDEFL_WRITE_ZLIB_HEADER) && (!d->m_block_index)) {
3078 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0x78, 8);
3079 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0x01, 8);
3080 }
3081
3082 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(flush == TDEFL_FINISH, 1);
3083
3084 pSaved_output_buf = d->m_pOutput_buf;
3085 saved_bit_buf = d->m_bit_buffer;
3086 saved_bits_in = d->m_bits_in;
3087
3088 if (!use_raw_block)
3089 comp_block_succeeded =
3090 tdefl_compress_block(d, (d->m_flags & TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_STATIC_BLOCKS) ||
3091 (d->m_total_lz_bytes < 48));
3092
3093 // If the block gets expanded, forget the current contents of the output
3094 // buffer and send a raw block instead.
3095 if (((use_raw_block) ||
3096 ((d->m_total_lz_bytes) && ((d->m_pOutput_buf - pSaved_output_buf + 1U) >=
3097 d->m_total_lz_bytes))) &&
3098 ((d->m_lookahead_pos - d->m_lz_code_buf_dict_pos) <= d->m_dict_size)) {
3099 mz_uint i;
3100 d->m_pOutput_buf = pSaved_output_buf;
3101 d->m_bit_buffer = saved_bit_buf, d->m_bits_in = saved_bits_in;
3102 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0, 2);
3103 if (d->m_bits_in) {
3104 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0, 8 - d->m_bits_in);
3105 }
3106 for (i = 2; i; --i, d->m_total_lz_bytes ^= 0xFFFF) {
3107 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(d->m_total_lz_bytes & 0xFFFF, 16);
3108 }
3109 for (i = 0; i < d->m_total_lz_bytes; ++i) {
3110 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(
3111 d->m_dict[(d->m_lz_code_buf_dict_pos + i) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK],
3112 8);
3113 }
3114 }
3115 // Check for the extremely unlikely (if not impossible) case of the compressed
3116 // block not fitting into the output buffer when using dynamic codes.
3117 else if (!comp_block_succeeded) {
3118 d->m_pOutput_buf = pSaved_output_buf;
3119 d->m_bit_buffer = saved_bit_buf, d->m_bits_in = saved_bits_in;
3120 tdefl_compress_block(d, MZ_TRUE);
3121 }
3122
3123 if (flush) {
3124 if (flush == TDEFL_FINISH) {
3125 if (d->m_bits_in) {
3126 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0, 8 - d->m_bits_in);
3127 }
3128 if (d->m_flags & TDEFL_WRITE_ZLIB_HEADER) {
3129 mz_uint i, a = d->m_adler32;
3130 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
3131 TDEFL_PUT_BITS((a >> 24) & 0xFF, 8);
3132 a <<= 8;
3133 }
3134 }
3135 } else {
3136 mz_uint i, z = 0;
3137 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0, 3);
3138 if (d->m_bits_in) {
3139 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(0, 8 - d->m_bits_in);
3140 }
3141 for (i = 2; i; --i, z ^= 0xFFFF) {
3142 TDEFL_PUT_BITS(z & 0xFFFF, 16);
3143 }
3144 }
3145 }
3146
3147 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_pOutput_buf < d->m_pOutput_buf_end);
3148
3149 memset(&d->m_huff_count[0][0], 0,
3150 sizeof(d->m_huff_count[0][0]) * TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_0);
3151 memset(&d->m_huff_count[1][0], 0,
3152 sizeof(d->m_huff_count[1][0]) * TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_1);
3153
3154 d->m_pLZ_code_buf = d->m_lz_code_buf + 1;
3155 d->m_pLZ_flags = d->m_lz_code_buf;
3156 d->m_num_flags_left = 8;
3157 d->m_lz_code_buf_dict_pos += d->m_total_lz_bytes;
3158 d->m_total_lz_bytes = 0;
3159 d->m_block_index++;
3160
3161 if ((n = (int)(d->m_pOutput_buf - pOutput_buf_start)) != 0) {
3162 if (d->m_pPut_buf_func) {
3163 *d->m_pIn_buf_size = d->m_pSrc - (const mz_uint8 *)d->m_pIn_buf;
3164 if (!(*d->m_pPut_buf_func)(d->m_output_buf, n, d->m_pPut_buf_user))
3165 return (d->m_prev_return_status = TDEFL_STATUS_PUT_BUF_FAILED);
3166 } else if (pOutput_buf_start == d->m_output_buf) {
3167 int bytes_to_copy = (int)MZ_MIN(
3168 (size_t)n, (size_t)(*d->m_pOut_buf_size - d->m_out_buf_ofs));
3169 memcpy((mz_uint8 *)d->m_pOut_buf + d->m_out_buf_ofs, d->m_output_buf,
3170 bytes_to_copy);
3171 d->m_out_buf_ofs += bytes_to_copy;
3172 if ((n -= bytes_to_copy) != 0) {
3173 d->m_output_flush_ofs = bytes_to_copy;
3174 d->m_output_flush_remaining = n;
3175 }
3176 } else {
3177 d->m_out_buf_ofs += n;
3178 }
3179 }
3180
3181 return d->m_output_flush_remaining;
3182}
3183
3184#if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES
3185#define TDEFL_READ_UNALIGNED_WORD(p) ((p)[0] | (p)[1] << 8)
3186static MZ_FORCEINLINE void
3187tdefl_find_match(tdefl_compressor *d, mz_uint lookahead_pos, mz_uint max_dist,
3188 mz_uint max_match_len, mz_uint *pMatch_dist,
3189 mz_uint *pMatch_len) {
3190 mz_uint dist, pos = lookahead_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK,
3191 match_len = *pMatch_len, probe_pos = pos, next_probe_pos,
3192 probe_len;
3193 mz_uint num_probes_left = d->m_max_probes[match_len >= 32];
3194 const mz_uint16 *s = (const mz_uint16 *)(d->m_dict + pos), *p, *q;
3195 mz_uint16 c01 = TDEFL_READ_UNALIGNED_WORD(&d->m_dict[pos + match_len - 1]),
3196 s01 = *s;
3197 MZ_ASSERT(max_match_len <= TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN);
3198 if (max_match_len <= match_len)
3199 return;
3200 for (;;) {
3201 for (;;) {
3202 if (--num_probes_left == 0)
3203 return;
3204#define TDEFL_PROBE \
3205 next_probe_pos = d->m_next[probe_pos]; \
3206 if ((!next_probe_pos) || \
3207 ((dist = (mz_uint16)(lookahead_pos - next_probe_pos)) > max_dist)) \
3208 return; \
3209 probe_pos = next_probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK; \
3210 if (TDEFL_READ_UNALIGNED_WORD(&d->m_dict[probe_pos + match_len - 1]) == c01) \
3211 break;
3212 TDEFL_PROBE;
3213 TDEFL_PROBE;
3214 TDEFL_PROBE;
3215 }
3216 if (!dist)
3217 break;
3218 q = (const mz_uint16 *)(d->m_dict + probe_pos);
3219 if (*q != s01)
3220 continue;
3221 p = s;
3222 probe_len = 32;
3223 do {
3224 } while ((*(++p) == *(++q)) && (*(++p) == *(++q)) && (*(++p) == *(++q)) &&
3225 (*(++p) == *(++q)) && (--probe_len > 0));
3226 if (!probe_len) {
3227 *pMatch_dist = dist;
3228 *pMatch_len = MZ_MIN(max_match_len, TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN);
3229 break;
3230 } else if ((probe_len = ((mz_uint)(p - s) * 2) +
3231 (mz_uint)(*(const mz_uint8 *)p ==
3232 *(const mz_uint8 *)q)) > match_len) {
3233 *pMatch_dist = dist;
3234 if ((*pMatch_len = match_len = MZ_MIN(max_match_len, probe_len)) ==
3235 max_match_len)
3236 break;
3237 c01 = TDEFL_READ_UNALIGNED_WORD(&d->m_dict[pos + match_len - 1]);
3238 }
3239 }
3240}
3241#else
3242static MZ_FORCEINLINE void
3243tdefl_find_match(tdefl_compressor *d, mz_uint lookahead_pos, mz_uint max_dist,
3244 mz_uint max_match_len, mz_uint *pMatch_dist,
3245 mz_uint *pMatch_len) {
3246 mz_uint dist, pos = lookahead_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK,
3247 match_len = *pMatch_len, probe_pos = pos, next_probe_pos,
3248 probe_len;
3249 mz_uint num_probes_left = d->m_max_probes[match_len >= 32];
3250 const mz_uint8 *s = d->m_dict + pos, *p, *q;
3251 mz_uint8 c0 = d->m_dict[pos + match_len], c1 = d->m_dict[pos + match_len - 1];
3252 MZ_ASSERT(max_match_len <= TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN);
3253 if (max_match_len <= match_len)
3254 return;
3255 for (;;) {
3256 for (;;) {
3257 if (--num_probes_left == 0)
3258 return;
3259#define TDEFL_PROBE \
3260 next_probe_pos = d->m_next[probe_pos]; \
3261 if ((!next_probe_pos) || \
3262 ((dist = (mz_uint16)(lookahead_pos - next_probe_pos)) > max_dist)) \
3263 return; \
3264 probe_pos = next_probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK; \
3265 if ((d->m_dict[probe_pos + match_len] == c0) && \
3266 (d->m_dict[probe_pos + match_len - 1] == c1)) \
3267 break;
3268 TDEFL_PROBE;
3269 TDEFL_PROBE;
3270 TDEFL_PROBE;
3271 }
3272 if (!dist)
3273 break;
3274 p = s;
3275 q = d->m_dict + probe_pos;
3276 for (probe_len = 0; probe_len < max_match_len; probe_len++)
3277 if (*p++ != *q++)
3278 break;
3279 if (probe_len > match_len) {
3280 *pMatch_dist = dist;
3281 if ((*pMatch_len = match_len = probe_len) == max_match_len)
3282 return;
3283 c0 = d->m_dict[pos + match_len];
3284 c1 = d->m_dict[pos + match_len - 1];
3285 }
3286 }
3287}
3288#endif // #if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES
3289
3290#if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN
3291static mz_bool tdefl_compress_fast(tdefl_compressor *d) {
3292 // Faster, minimally featured LZRW1-style match+parse loop with better
3293 // register utilization. Intended for applications where raw throughput is
3294 // valued more highly than ratio.
3295 mz_uint lookahead_pos = d->m_lookahead_pos,
3296 lookahead_size = d->m_lookahead_size, dict_size = d->m_dict_size,
3297 total_lz_bytes = d->m_total_lz_bytes,
3298 num_flags_left = d->m_num_flags_left;
3299 mz_uint8 *pLZ_code_buf = d->m_pLZ_code_buf, *pLZ_flags = d->m_pLZ_flags;
3300 mz_uint cur_pos = lookahead_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3301
3302 while ((d->m_src_buf_left) || ((d->m_flush) && (lookahead_size))) {
3303 const mz_uint TDEFL_COMP_FAST_LOOKAHEAD_SIZE = 4096;
3304 mz_uint dst_pos =
3305 (lookahead_pos + lookahead_size) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3306 mz_uint num_bytes_to_process = (mz_uint)MZ_MIN(
3307 d->m_src_buf_left, TDEFL_COMP_FAST_LOOKAHEAD_SIZE - lookahead_size);
3308 d->m_src_buf_left -= num_bytes_to_process;
3309 lookahead_size += num_bytes_to_process;
3310
3311 while (num_bytes_to_process) {
3312 mz_uint32 n = MZ_MIN(TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - dst_pos, num_bytes_to_process);
3313 memcpy(d->m_dict + dst_pos, d->m_pSrc, n);
3314 if (dst_pos < (TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN - 1))
3315 memcpy(d->m_dict + TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE + dst_pos, d->m_pSrc,
3316 MZ_MIN(n, (TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN - 1) - dst_pos));
3317 d->m_pSrc += n;
3318 dst_pos = (dst_pos + n) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3319 num_bytes_to_process -= n;
3320 }
3321
3322 dict_size = MZ_MIN(TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - lookahead_size, dict_size);
3323 if ((!d->m_flush) && (lookahead_size < TDEFL_COMP_FAST_LOOKAHEAD_SIZE))
3324 break;
3325
3326 while (lookahead_size >= 4) {
3327 mz_uint cur_match_dist, cur_match_len = 1;
3328 mz_uint8 *pCur_dict = d->m_dict + cur_pos;
3329 mz_uint first_trigram = (*(const mz_uint32 *)pCur_dict) & 0xFFFFFF;
3330 mz_uint hash =
3331 (first_trigram ^ (first_trigram >> (24 - (TDEFL_LZ_HASH_BITS - 8)))) &
3332 TDEFL_LEVEL1_HASH_SIZE_MASK;
3333 mz_uint probe_pos = d->m_hash[hash];
3334 d->m_hash[hash] = (mz_uint16)lookahead_pos;
3335
3336 if (((cur_match_dist = (mz_uint16)(lookahead_pos - probe_pos)) <=
3337 dict_size) &&
3338 ((mz_uint32)(
3339 *(d->m_dict + (probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK)) |
3340 (*(d->m_dict + ((probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK) + 1))
3341 << 8) |
3342 (*(d->m_dict + ((probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK) + 2))
3343 << 16)) == first_trigram)) {
3344 const mz_uint16 *p = (const mz_uint16 *)pCur_dict;
3345 const mz_uint16 *q =
3346 (const mz_uint16 *)(d->m_dict +
3347 (probe_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK));
3348 mz_uint32 probe_len = 32;
3349 do {
3350 } while ((*(++p) == *(++q)) && (*(++p) == *(++q)) &&
3351 (*(++p) == *(++q)) && (*(++p) == *(++q)) && (--probe_len > 0));
3352 cur_match_len = ((mz_uint)(p - (const mz_uint16 *)pCur_dict) * 2) +
3353 (mz_uint)(*(const mz_uint8 *)p == *(const mz_uint8 *)q);
3354 if (!probe_len)
3355 cur_match_len = cur_match_dist ? TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN : 0;
3356
3357 if ((cur_match_len < TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) ||
3358 ((cur_match_len == TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) &&
3359 (cur_match_dist >= 8U * 1024U))) {
3360 cur_match_len = 1;
3361 *pLZ_code_buf++ = (mz_uint8)first_trigram;
3362 *pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)(*pLZ_flags >> 1);
3363 d->m_huff_count[0][(mz_uint8)first_trigram]++;
3364 } else {
3365 mz_uint32 s0, s1;
3366 cur_match_len = MZ_MIN(cur_match_len, lookahead_size);
3367
3368 MZ_ASSERT((cur_match_len >= TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) &&
3369 (cur_match_dist >= 1) &&
3370 (cur_match_dist <= TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE));
3371
3372 cur_match_dist--;
3373
3374 pLZ_code_buf[0] = (mz_uint8)(cur_match_len - TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN);
3375 *(mz_uint16 *)(&pLZ_code_buf[1]) = (mz_uint16)cur_match_dist;
3376 pLZ_code_buf += 3;
3377 *pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)((*pLZ_flags >> 1) | 0x80);
3378
3379 s0 = s_tdefl_small_dist_sym[cur_match_dist & 511];
3380 s1 = s_tdefl_large_dist_sym[cur_match_dist >> 8];
3381 d->m_huff_count[1][(cur_match_dist < 512) ? s0 : s1]++;
3382
3383 d->m_huff_count[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[cur_match_len -
3384 TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN]]++;
3385 }
3386 } else {
3387 *pLZ_code_buf++ = (mz_uint8)first_trigram;
3388 *pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)(*pLZ_flags >> 1);
3389 d->m_huff_count[0][(mz_uint8)first_trigram]++;
3390 }
3391
3392 if (--num_flags_left == 0) {
3393 num_flags_left = 8;
3394 pLZ_flags = pLZ_code_buf++;
3395 }
3396
3397 total_lz_bytes += cur_match_len;
3398 lookahead_pos += cur_match_len;
3399 dict_size = MZ_MIN(dict_size + cur_match_len, TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE);
3400 cur_pos = (cur_pos + cur_match_len) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3401 MZ_ASSERT(lookahead_size >= cur_match_len);
3402 lookahead_size -= cur_match_len;
3403
3404 if (pLZ_code_buf > &d->m_lz_code_buf[TDEFL_LZ_CODE_BUF_SIZE - 8]) {
3405 int n;
3406 d->m_lookahead_pos = lookahead_pos;
3407 d->m_lookahead_size = lookahead_size;
3408 d->m_dict_size = dict_size;
3409 d->m_total_lz_bytes = total_lz_bytes;
3410 d->m_pLZ_code_buf = pLZ_code_buf;
3411 d->m_pLZ_flags = pLZ_flags;
3412 d->m_num_flags_left = num_flags_left;
3413 if ((n = tdefl_flush_block(d, 0)) != 0)
3414 return (n < 0) ? MZ_FALSE : MZ_TRUE;
3415 total_lz_bytes = d->m_total_lz_bytes;
3416 pLZ_code_buf = d->m_pLZ_code_buf;
3417 pLZ_flags = d->m_pLZ_flags;
3418 num_flags_left = d->m_num_flags_left;
3419 }
3420 }
3421
3422 while (lookahead_size) {
3423 mz_uint8 lit = d->m_dict[cur_pos];
3424
3425 total_lz_bytes++;
3426 *pLZ_code_buf++ = lit;
3427 *pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)(*pLZ_flags >> 1);
3428 if (--num_flags_left == 0) {
3429 num_flags_left = 8;
3430 pLZ_flags = pLZ_code_buf++;
3431 }
3432
3433 d->m_huff_count[0][lit]++;
3434
3435 lookahead_pos++;
3436 dict_size = MZ_MIN(dict_size + 1, TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE);
3437 cur_pos = (cur_pos + 1) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3438 lookahead_size--;
3439
3440 if (pLZ_code_buf > &d->m_lz_code_buf[TDEFL_LZ_CODE_BUF_SIZE - 8]) {
3441 int n;
3442 d->m_lookahead_pos = lookahead_pos;
3443 d->m_lookahead_size = lookahead_size;
3444 d->m_dict_size = dict_size;
3445 d->m_total_lz_bytes = total_lz_bytes;
3446 d->m_pLZ_code_buf = pLZ_code_buf;
3447 d->m_pLZ_flags = pLZ_flags;
3448 d->m_num_flags_left = num_flags_left;
3449 if ((n = tdefl_flush_block(d, 0)) != 0)
3450 return (n < 0) ? MZ_FALSE : MZ_TRUE;
3451 total_lz_bytes = d->m_total_lz_bytes;
3452 pLZ_code_buf = d->m_pLZ_code_buf;
3453 pLZ_flags = d->m_pLZ_flags;
3454 num_flags_left = d->m_num_flags_left;
3455 }
3456 }
3457 }
3458
3459 d->m_lookahead_pos = lookahead_pos;
3460 d->m_lookahead_size = lookahead_size;
3461 d->m_dict_size = dict_size;
3462 d->m_total_lz_bytes = total_lz_bytes;
3463 d->m_pLZ_code_buf = pLZ_code_buf;
3464 d->m_pLZ_flags = pLZ_flags;
3465 d->m_num_flags_left = num_flags_left;
3466 return MZ_TRUE;
3467}
3468#endif // MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN
3469
3470static MZ_FORCEINLINE void tdefl_record_literal(tdefl_compressor *d,
3471 mz_uint8 lit) {
3472 d->m_total_lz_bytes++;
3473 *d->m_pLZ_code_buf++ = lit;
3474 *d->m_pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)(*d->m_pLZ_flags >> 1);
3475 if (--d->m_num_flags_left == 0) {
3476 d->m_num_flags_left = 8;
3477 d->m_pLZ_flags = d->m_pLZ_code_buf++;
3478 }
3479 d->m_huff_count[0][lit]++;
3480}
3481
3482static MZ_FORCEINLINE void
3483tdefl_record_match(tdefl_compressor *d, mz_uint match_len, mz_uint match_dist) {
3484 mz_uint32 s0, s1;
3485
3486 MZ_ASSERT((match_len >= TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) && (match_dist >= 1) &&
3487 (match_dist <= TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE));
3488
3489 d->m_total_lz_bytes += match_len;
3490
3491 d->m_pLZ_code_buf[0] = (mz_uint8)(match_len - TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN);
3492
3493 match_dist -= 1;
3494 d->m_pLZ_code_buf[1] = (mz_uint8)(match_dist & 0xFF);
3495 d->m_pLZ_code_buf[2] = (mz_uint8)(match_dist >> 8);
3496 d->m_pLZ_code_buf += 3;
3497
3498 *d->m_pLZ_flags = (mz_uint8)((*d->m_pLZ_flags >> 1) | 0x80);
3499 if (--d->m_num_flags_left == 0) {
3500 d->m_num_flags_left = 8;
3501 d->m_pLZ_flags = d->m_pLZ_code_buf++;
3502 }
3503
3504 s0 = s_tdefl_small_dist_sym[match_dist & 511];
3505 s1 = s_tdefl_large_dist_sym[(match_dist >> 8) & 127];
3506 d->m_huff_count[1][(match_dist < 512) ? s0 : s1]++;
3507
3508 if (match_len >= TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN)
3509 d->m_huff_count[0][s_tdefl_len_sym[match_len - TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN]]++;
3510}
3511
3512static mz_bool tdefl_compress_normal(tdefl_compressor *d) {
3513 const mz_uint8 *pSrc = d->m_pSrc;
3514 size_t src_buf_left = d->m_src_buf_left;
3515 tdefl_flush flush = d->m_flush;
3516
3517 while ((src_buf_left) || ((flush) && (d->m_lookahead_size))) {
3518 mz_uint len_to_move, cur_match_dist, cur_match_len, cur_pos;
3519 // Update dictionary and hash chains. Keeps the lookahead size equal to
3520 // TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN.
3521 if ((d->m_lookahead_size + d->m_dict_size) >= (TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN - 1)) {
3522 mz_uint dst_pos = (d->m_lookahead_pos + d->m_lookahead_size) &
3523 TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK,
3524 ins_pos = d->m_lookahead_pos + d->m_lookahead_size - 2;
3525 mz_uint hash = (d->m_dict[ins_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK]
3526 << TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SHIFT) ^
3527 d->m_dict[(ins_pos + 1) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK];
3528 mz_uint num_bytes_to_process = (mz_uint)MZ_MIN(
3529 src_buf_left, TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN - d->m_lookahead_size);
3530 const mz_uint8 *pSrc_end = pSrc + num_bytes_to_process;
3531 src_buf_left -= num_bytes_to_process;
3532 d->m_lookahead_size += num_bytes_to_process;
3533 while (pSrc != pSrc_end) {
3534 mz_uint8 c = *pSrc++;
3535 d->m_dict[dst_pos] = c;
3536 if (dst_pos < (TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN - 1))
3537 d->m_dict[TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE + dst_pos] = c;
3538 hash = ((hash << TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SHIFT) ^ c) & (TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SIZE - 1);
3539 d->m_next[ins_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK] = d->m_hash[hash];
3540 d->m_hash[hash] = (mz_uint16)(ins_pos);
3541 dst_pos = (dst_pos + 1) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3542 ins_pos++;
3543 }
3544 } else {
3545 while ((src_buf_left) && (d->m_lookahead_size < TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN)) {
3546 mz_uint8 c = *pSrc++;
3547 mz_uint dst_pos = (d->m_lookahead_pos + d->m_lookahead_size) &
3548 TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3549 src_buf_left--;
3550 d->m_dict[dst_pos] = c;
3551 if (dst_pos < (TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN - 1))
3552 d->m_dict[TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE + dst_pos] = c;
3553 if ((++d->m_lookahead_size + d->m_dict_size) >= TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) {
3554 mz_uint ins_pos = d->m_lookahead_pos + (d->m_lookahead_size - 1) - 2;
3555 mz_uint hash = ((d->m_dict[ins_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK]
3556 << (TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SHIFT * 2)) ^
3557 (d->m_dict[(ins_pos + 1) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK]
3558 << TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SHIFT) ^
3559 c) &
3560 (TDEFL_LZ_HASH_SIZE - 1);
3561 d->m_next[ins_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK] = d->m_hash[hash];
3562 d->m_hash[hash] = (mz_uint16)(ins_pos);
3563 }
3564 }
3565 }
3566 d->m_dict_size =
3567 MZ_MIN(TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - d->m_lookahead_size, d->m_dict_size);
3568 if ((!flush) && (d->m_lookahead_size < TDEFL_MAX_MATCH_LEN))
3569 break;
3570
3571 // Simple lazy/greedy parsing state machine.
3572 len_to_move = 1;
3573 cur_match_dist = 0;
3574 cur_match_len =
3575 d->m_saved_match_len ? d->m_saved_match_len : (TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN - 1);
3576 cur_pos = d->m_lookahead_pos & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK;
3577 if (d->m_flags & (TDEFL_RLE_MATCHES | TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS)) {
3578 if ((d->m_dict_size) && (!(d->m_flags & TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS))) {
3579 mz_uint8 c = d->m_dict[(cur_pos - 1) & TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE_MASK];
3580 cur_match_len = 0;
3581 while (cur_match_len < d->m_lookahead_size) {
3582 if (d->m_dict[cur_pos + cur_match_len] != c)
3583 break;
3584 cur_match_len++;
3585 }
3586 if (cur_match_len < TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN)
3587 cur_match_len = 0;
3588 else
3589 cur_match_dist = 1;
3590 }
3591 } else {
3592 tdefl_find_match(d, d->m_lookahead_pos, d->m_dict_size,
3593 d->m_lookahead_size, &cur_match_dist, &cur_match_len);
3594 }
3595 if (((cur_match_len == TDEFL_MIN_MATCH_LEN) &&
3596 (cur_match_dist >= 8U * 1024U)) ||
3597 (cur_pos == cur_match_dist) ||
3598 ((d->m_flags & TDEFL_FILTER_MATCHES) && (cur_match_len <= 5))) {
3599 cur_match_dist = cur_match_len = 0;
3600 }
3601 if (d->m_saved_match_len) {
3602 if (cur_match_len > d->m_saved_match_len) {
3603 tdefl_record_literal(d, (mz_uint8)d->m_saved_lit);
3604 if (cur_match_len >= 128) {
3605 tdefl_record_match(d, cur_match_len, cur_match_dist);
3606 d->m_saved_match_len = 0;
3607 len_to_move = cur_match_len;
3608 } else {
3609 d->m_saved_lit = d->m_dict[cur_pos];
3610 d->m_saved_match_dist = cur_match_dist;
3611 d->m_saved_match_len = cur_match_len;
3612 }
3613 } else {
3614 tdefl_record_match(d, d->m_saved_match_len, d->m_saved_match_dist);
3615 len_to_move = d->m_saved_match_len - 1;
3616 d->m_saved_match_len = 0;
3617 }
3618 } else if (!cur_match_dist)
3619 tdefl_record_literal(d,
3620 d->m_dict[MZ_MIN(cur_pos, sizeof(d->m_dict) - 1)]);
3621 else if ((d->m_greedy_parsing) || (d->m_flags & TDEFL_RLE_MATCHES) ||
3622 (cur_match_len >= 128)) {
3623 tdefl_record_match(d, cur_match_len, cur_match_dist);
3624 len_to_move = cur_match_len;
3625 } else {
3626 d->m_saved_lit = d->m_dict[MZ_MIN(cur_pos, sizeof(d->m_dict) - 1)];
3627 d->m_saved_match_dist = cur_match_dist;
3628 d->m_saved_match_len = cur_match_len;
3629 }
3630 // Move the lookahead forward by len_to_move bytes.
3631 d->m_lookahead_pos += len_to_move;
3632 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_lookahead_size >= len_to_move);
3633 d->m_lookahead_size -= len_to_move;
3634 d->m_dict_size = MZ_MIN(d->m_dict_size + len_to_move, TDEFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE);
3635 // Check if it's time to flush the current LZ codes to the internal output
3636 // buffer.
3637 if ((d->m_pLZ_code_buf > &d->m_lz_code_buf[TDEFL_LZ_CODE_BUF_SIZE - 8]) ||
3638 ((d->m_total_lz_bytes > 31 * 1024) &&
3639 (((((mz_uint)(d->m_pLZ_code_buf - d->m_lz_code_buf) * 115) >> 7) >=
3640 d->m_total_lz_bytes) ||
3641 (d->m_flags & TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS)))) {
3642 int n;
3643 d->m_pSrc = pSrc;
3644 d->m_src_buf_left = src_buf_left;
3645 if ((n = tdefl_flush_block(d, 0)) != 0)
3646 return (n < 0) ? MZ_FALSE : MZ_TRUE;
3647 }
3648 }
3649
3650 d->m_pSrc = pSrc;
3651 d->m_src_buf_left = src_buf_left;
3652 return MZ_TRUE;
3653}
3654
3655static tdefl_status tdefl_flush_output_buffer(tdefl_compressor *d) {
3656 if (d->m_pIn_buf_size) {
3657 *d->m_pIn_buf_size = d->m_pSrc - (const mz_uint8 *)d->m_pIn_buf;
3658 }
3659
3660 if (d->m_pOut_buf_size) {
3661 size_t n = MZ_MIN(*d->m_pOut_buf_size - d->m_out_buf_ofs,
3662 d->m_output_flush_remaining);
3663 memcpy((mz_uint8 *)d->m_pOut_buf + d->m_out_buf_ofs,
3664 d->m_output_buf + d->m_output_flush_ofs, n);
3665 d->m_output_flush_ofs += (mz_uint)n;
3666 d->m_output_flush_remaining -= (mz_uint)n;
3667 d->m_out_buf_ofs += n;
3668
3669 *d->m_pOut_buf_size = d->m_out_buf_ofs;
3670 }
3671
3672 return (d->m_finished && !d->m_output_flush_remaining) ? TDEFL_STATUS_DONE
3673 : TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY;
3674}
3675
3676tdefl_status tdefl_compress(tdefl_compressor *d, const void *pIn_buf,
3677 size_t *pIn_buf_size, void *pOut_buf,
3678 size_t *pOut_buf_size, tdefl_flush flush) {
3679 if (!d) {
3680 if (pIn_buf_size)
3681 *pIn_buf_size = 0;
3682 if (pOut_buf_size)
3683 *pOut_buf_size = 0;
3684 return TDEFL_STATUS_BAD_PARAM;
3685 }
3686
3687 d->m_pIn_buf = pIn_buf;
3688 d->m_pIn_buf_size = pIn_buf_size;
3689 d->m_pOut_buf = pOut_buf;
3690 d->m_pOut_buf_size = pOut_buf_size;
3691 d->m_pSrc = (const mz_uint8 *)(pIn_buf);
3692 d->m_src_buf_left = pIn_buf_size ? *pIn_buf_size : 0;
3693 d->m_out_buf_ofs = 0;
3694 d->m_flush = flush;
3695
3696 if (((d->m_pPut_buf_func != NULL) ==
3697 ((pOut_buf != NULL) || (pOut_buf_size != NULL))) ||
3698 (d->m_prev_return_status != TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY) ||
3699 (d->m_wants_to_finish && (flush != TDEFL_FINISH)) ||
3700 (pIn_buf_size && *pIn_buf_size && !pIn_buf) ||
3701 (pOut_buf_size && *pOut_buf_size && !pOut_buf)) {
3702 if (pIn_buf_size)
3703 *pIn_buf_size = 0;
3704 if (pOut_buf_size)
3705 *pOut_buf_size = 0;
3706 return (d->m_prev_return_status = TDEFL_STATUS_BAD_PARAM);
3707 }
3708 d->m_wants_to_finish |= (flush == TDEFL_FINISH);
3709
3710 if ((d->m_output_flush_remaining) || (d->m_finished))
3711 return (d->m_prev_return_status = tdefl_flush_output_buffer(d));
3712
3713#if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN
3714 if (((d->m_flags & TDEFL_MAX_PROBES_MASK) == 1) &&
3715 ((d->m_flags & TDEFL_GREEDY_PARSING_FLAG) != 0) &&
3716 ((d->m_flags & (TDEFL_FILTER_MATCHES | TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS |
3717 TDEFL_RLE_MATCHES)) == 0)) {
3718 if (!tdefl_compress_fast(d))
3719 return d->m_prev_return_status;
3720 } else
3721#endif // #if MINIZ_USE_UNALIGNED_LOADS_AND_STORES && MINIZ_LITTLE_ENDIAN
3722 {
3723 if (!tdefl_compress_normal(d))
3724 return d->m_prev_return_status;
3725 }
3726
3727 if ((d->m_flags & (TDEFL_WRITE_ZLIB_HEADER | TDEFL_COMPUTE_ADLER32)) &&
3728 (pIn_buf))
3729 d->m_adler32 =
3730 (mz_uint32)mz_adler32(d->m_adler32, (const mz_uint8 *)pIn_buf,
3731 d->m_pSrc - (const mz_uint8 *)pIn_buf);
3732
3733 if ((flush) && (!d->m_lookahead_size) && (!d->m_src_buf_left) &&
3734 (!d->m_output_flush_remaining)) {
3735 if (tdefl_flush_block(d, flush) < 0)
3736 return d->m_prev_return_status;
3737 d->m_finished = (flush == TDEFL_FINISH);
3738 if (flush == TDEFL_FULL_FLUSH) {
3739 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(d->m_hash);
3740 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(d->m_next);
3741 d->m_dict_size = 0;
3742 }
3743 }
3744
3745 return (d->m_prev_return_status = tdefl_flush_output_buffer(d));
3746}
3747
3748tdefl_status tdefl_compress_buffer(tdefl_compressor *d, const void *pIn_buf,
3749 size_t in_buf_size, tdefl_flush flush) {
3750 MZ_ASSERT(d->m_pPut_buf_func);
3751 return tdefl_compress(d, pIn_buf, &in_buf_size, NULL, NULL, flush);
3752}
3753
3754tdefl_status tdefl_init(tdefl_compressor *d,
3755 tdefl_put_buf_func_ptr pPut_buf_func,
3756 void *pPut_buf_user, int flags) {
3757 d->m_pPut_buf_func = pPut_buf_func;
3758 d->m_pPut_buf_user = pPut_buf_user;
3759 d->m_flags = (mz_uint)(flags);
3760 d->m_max_probes[0] = 1 + ((flags & 0xFFF) + 2) / 3;
3761 d->m_greedy_parsing = (flags & TDEFL_GREEDY_PARSING_FLAG) != 0;
3762 d->m_max_probes[1] = 1 + (((flags & 0xFFF) >> 2) + 2) / 3;
3763 if (!(flags & TDEFL_NONDETERMINISTIC_PARSING_FLAG))
3764 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(d->m_hash);
3765 d->m_lookahead_pos = d->m_lookahead_size = d->m_dict_size =
3766 d->m_total_lz_bytes = d->m_lz_code_buf_dict_pos = d->m_bits_in = 0;
3767 d->m_output_flush_ofs = d->m_output_flush_remaining = d->m_finished =
3768 d->m_block_index = d->m_bit_buffer = d->m_wants_to_finish = 0;
3769 d->m_pLZ_code_buf = d->m_lz_code_buf + 1;
3770 d->m_pLZ_flags = d->m_lz_code_buf;
3771 d->m_num_flags_left = 8;
3772 d->m_pOutput_buf = d->m_output_buf;
3773 d->m_pOutput_buf_end = d->m_output_buf;
3774 d->m_prev_return_status = TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY;
3775 d->m_saved_match_dist = d->m_saved_match_len = d->m_saved_lit = 0;
3776 d->m_adler32 = 1;
3777 d->m_pIn_buf = NULL;
3778 d->m_pOut_buf = NULL;
3779 d->m_pIn_buf_size = NULL;
3780 d->m_pOut_buf_size = NULL;
3781 d->m_flush = TDEFL_NO_FLUSH;
3782 d->m_pSrc = NULL;
3783 d->m_src_buf_left = 0;
3784 d->m_out_buf_ofs = 0;
3785 memset(&d->m_huff_count[0][0], 0,
3786 sizeof(d->m_huff_count[0][0]) * TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_0);
3787 memset(&d->m_huff_count[1][0], 0,
3788 sizeof(d->m_huff_count[1][0]) * TDEFL_MAX_HUFF_SYMBOLS_1);
3789 return TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY;
3790}
3791
3792tdefl_status tdefl_get_prev_return_status(tdefl_compressor *d) {
3793 return d->m_prev_return_status;
3794}
3795
3796mz_uint32 tdefl_get_adler32(tdefl_compressor *d) { return d->m_adler32; }
3797
3798mz_bool tdefl_compress_mem_to_output(const void *pBuf, size_t buf_len,
3799 tdefl_put_buf_func_ptr pPut_buf_func,
3800 void *pPut_buf_user, int flags) {
3801 tdefl_compressor *pComp;
3802 mz_bool succeeded;
3803 if (((buf_len) && (!pBuf)) || (!pPut_buf_func))
3804 return MZ_FALSE;
3805 pComp = (tdefl_compressor *)MZ_MALLOC(sizeof(tdefl_compressor));
3806 if (!pComp)
3807 return MZ_FALSE;
3808 succeeded = (tdefl_init(pComp, pPut_buf_func, pPut_buf_user, flags) ==
3809 TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY);
3810 succeeded =
3811 succeeded && (tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp, pBuf, buf_len, TDEFL_FINISH) ==
3812 TDEFL_STATUS_DONE);
3813 MZ_FREE(pComp);
3814 return succeeded;
3815}
3816
3817typedef struct {
3818 size_t m_size, m_capacity;
3819 mz_uint8 *m_pBuf;
3820 mz_bool m_expandable;
3821} tdefl_output_buffer;
3822
3823static mz_bool tdefl_output_buffer_putter(const void *pBuf, int len,
3824 void *pUser) {
3825 tdefl_output_buffer *p = (tdefl_output_buffer *)pUser;
3826 size_t new_size = p->m_size + len;
3827 if (new_size > p->m_capacity) {
3828 size_t new_capacity = p->m_capacity;
3829 mz_uint8 *pNew_buf;
3830 if (!p->m_expandable)
3831 return MZ_FALSE;
3832 do {
3833 new_capacity = MZ_MAX(128U, new_capacity << 1U);
3834 } while (new_size > new_capacity);
3835 pNew_buf = (mz_uint8 *)MZ_REALLOC(p->m_pBuf, new_capacity);
3836 if (!pNew_buf)
3837 return MZ_FALSE;
3838 p->m_pBuf = pNew_buf;
3839 p->m_capacity = new_capacity;
3840 }
3841 memcpy((mz_uint8 *)p->m_pBuf + p->m_size, pBuf, len);
3842 p->m_size = new_size;
3843 return MZ_TRUE;
3844}
3845
3846void *tdefl_compress_mem_to_heap(const void *pSrc_buf, size_t src_buf_len,
3847 size_t *pOut_len, int flags) {
3848 tdefl_output_buffer out_buf;
3849 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(out_buf);
3850 if (!pOut_len)
3851 return MZ_FALSE;
3852 else
3853 *pOut_len = 0;
3854 out_buf.m_expandable = MZ_TRUE;
3855 if (!tdefl_compress_mem_to_output(
3856 pSrc_buf, src_buf_len, tdefl_output_buffer_putter, &out_buf, flags))
3857 return NULL;
3858 *pOut_len = out_buf.m_size;
3859 return out_buf.m_pBuf;
3860}
3861
3862size_t tdefl_compress_mem_to_mem(void *pOut_buf, size_t out_buf_len,
3863 const void *pSrc_buf, size_t src_buf_len,
3864 int flags) {
3865 tdefl_output_buffer out_buf;
3866 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(out_buf);
3867 if (!pOut_buf)
3868 return 0;
3869 out_buf.m_pBuf = (mz_uint8 *)pOut_buf;
3870 out_buf.m_capacity = out_buf_len;
3871 if (!tdefl_compress_mem_to_output(
3872 pSrc_buf, src_buf_len, tdefl_output_buffer_putter, &out_buf, flags))
3873 return 0;
3874 return out_buf.m_size;
3875}
3876
3877#ifndef MINIZ_NO_ZLIB_APIS
3878static const mz_uint s_tdefl_num_probes[11] = {0, 1, 6, 32, 16, 32,
3879 128, 256, 512, 768, 1500};
3880
3881// level may actually range from [0,10] (10 is a "hidden" max level, where we
3882// want a bit more compression and it's fine if throughput to fall off a cliff
3883// on some files).
3884mz_uint tdefl_create_comp_flags_from_zip_params(int level, int window_bits,
3885 int strategy) {
3886 mz_uint comp_flags =
3887 s_tdefl_num_probes[(level >= 0) ? MZ_MIN(10, level) : MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL] |
3888 ((level <= 3) ? TDEFL_GREEDY_PARSING_FLAG : 0);
3889 if (window_bits > 0)
3890 comp_flags |= TDEFL_WRITE_ZLIB_HEADER;
3891
3892 if (!level)
3893 comp_flags |= TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_RAW_BLOCKS;
3894 else if (strategy == MZ_FILTERED)
3895 comp_flags |= TDEFL_FILTER_MATCHES;
3896 else if (strategy == MZ_HUFFMAN_ONLY)
3897 comp_flags &= ~TDEFL_MAX_PROBES_MASK;
3898 else if (strategy == MZ_FIXED)
3899 comp_flags |= TDEFL_FORCE_ALL_STATIC_BLOCKS;
3900 else if (strategy == MZ_RLE)
3901 comp_flags |= TDEFL_RLE_MATCHES;
3902
3903 return comp_flags;
3904}
3905#endif // MINIZ_NO_ZLIB_APIS
3906
3907#ifdef _MSC_VER
3908#pragma warning(push)
3909#pragma warning(disable : 4204) // nonstandard extension used : non-constant
3910 // aggregate initializer (also supported by GNU
3911 // C and C99, so no big deal)
3912#endif
3913
3914// Simple PNG writer function by Alex Evans, 2011. Released into the public
3915// domain: https://gist.github.com/908299, more context at
3916// http://altdevblogaday.org/2011/04/06/a-smaller-jpg-encoder/.
3917// This is actually a modification of Alex's original code so PNG files
3918// generated by this function pass pngcheck.
3919void *tdefl_write_image_to_png_file_in_memory_ex(const void *pImage, int w,
3920 int h, int num_chans,
3921 size_t *pLen_out,
3922 mz_uint level, mz_bool flip) {
3923 // Using a local copy of this array here in case MINIZ_NO_ZLIB_APIS was
3924 // defined.
3925 static const mz_uint s_tdefl_png_num_probes[11] = {
3926 0, 1, 6, 32, 16, 32, 128, 256, 512, 768, 1500};
3927 tdefl_compressor *pComp =
3928 (tdefl_compressor *)MZ_MALLOC(sizeof(tdefl_compressor));
3929 tdefl_output_buffer out_buf;
3930 int i, bpl = w * num_chans, y, z;
3931 mz_uint32 c;
3932 *pLen_out = 0;
3933 if (!pComp)
3934 return NULL;
3935 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(out_buf);
3936 out_buf.m_expandable = MZ_TRUE;
3937 out_buf.m_capacity = 57 + MZ_MAX(64, (1 + bpl) * h);
3938 if (NULL == (out_buf.m_pBuf = (mz_uint8 *)MZ_MALLOC(out_buf.m_capacity))) {
3939 MZ_FREE(pComp);
3940 return NULL;
3941 }
3942 // write dummy header
3943 for (z = 41; z; --z)
3944 tdefl_output_buffer_putter(&z, 1, &out_buf);
3945 // compress image data
3946 tdefl_init(pComp, tdefl_output_buffer_putter, &out_buf,
3947 s_tdefl_png_num_probes[MZ_MIN(10, level)] |
3948 TDEFL_WRITE_ZLIB_HEADER);
3949 for (y = 0; y < h; ++y) {
3950 tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp, &z, 1, TDEFL_NO_FLUSH);
3951 tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp,
3952 (mz_uint8 *)pImage + (flip ? (h - 1 - y) : y) * bpl,
3953 bpl, TDEFL_NO_FLUSH);
3954 }
3955 if (tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp, NULL, 0, TDEFL_FINISH) !=
3956 TDEFL_STATUS_DONE) {
3957 MZ_FREE(pComp);
3958 MZ_FREE(out_buf.m_pBuf);
3959 return NULL;
3960 }
3961 // write real header
3962 *pLen_out = out_buf.m_size - 41;
3963 {
3964 static const mz_uint8 chans[] = {0x00, 0x00, 0x04, 0x02, 0x06};
3965 mz_uint8 pnghdr[41] = {0x89,
3966 0x50,
3967 0x4e,
3968 0x47,
3969 0x0d,
3970 0x0a,
3971 0x1a,
3972 0x0a,
3973 0x00,
3974 0x00,
3975 0x00,
3976 0x0d,
3977 0x49,
3978 0x48,
3979 0x44,
3980 0x52,
3981 0,
3982 0,
3983 (mz_uint8)(w >> 8),
3984 (mz_uint8)w,
3985 0,
3986 0,
3987 (mz_uint8)(h >> 8),
3988 (mz_uint8)h,
3989 8,
3990 chans[num_chans],
3991 0,
3992 0,
3993 0,
3994 0,
3995 0,
3996 0,
3997 0,
3998 (mz_uint8)(*pLen_out >> 24),
3999 (mz_uint8)(*pLen_out >> 16),
4000 (mz_uint8)(*pLen_out >> 8),
4001 (mz_uint8)*pLen_out,
4002 0x49,
4003 0x44,
4004 0x41,
4005 0x54};
4006 c = (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(MZ_CRC32_INIT, pnghdr + 12, 17);
4007 for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i, c <<= 8)
4008 ((mz_uint8 *)(pnghdr + 29))[i] = (mz_uint8)(c >> 24);
4009 memcpy(out_buf.m_pBuf, pnghdr, 41);
4010 }
4011 // write footer (IDAT CRC-32, followed by IEND chunk)
4012 if (!tdefl_output_buffer_putter(
4013 "\0\0\0\0\0\0\0\0\x49\x45\x4e\x44\xae\x42\x60\x82", 16, &out_buf)) {
4014 *pLen_out = 0;
4015 MZ_FREE(pComp);
4016 MZ_FREE(out_buf.m_pBuf);
4017 return NULL;
4018 }
4019 c = (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(MZ_CRC32_INIT, out_buf.m_pBuf + 41 - 4,
4020 *pLen_out + 4);
4021 for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i, c <<= 8)
4022 (out_buf.m_pBuf + out_buf.m_size - 16)[i] = (mz_uint8)(c >> 24);
4023 // compute final size of file, grab compressed data buffer and return
4024 *pLen_out += 57;
4025 MZ_FREE(pComp);
4026 return out_buf.m_pBuf;
4027}
4028void *tdefl_write_image_to_png_file_in_memory(const void *pImage, int w, int h,
4029 int num_chans, size_t *pLen_out) {
4030 // Level 6 corresponds to TDEFL_DEFAULT_MAX_PROBES or MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL (but we
4031 // can't depend on MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL being available in case the zlib API's
4032 // where #defined out)
4033 return tdefl_write_image_to_png_file_in_memory_ex(pImage, w, h, num_chans,
4034 pLen_out, 6, MZ_FALSE);
4035}

4038#pragma warning(pop)

4204typedef struct {

4210struct mz_zip_internal_state_tag {
4211 mz_zip_array m_central_dir;
4212 mz_zip_array m_central_dir_offsets;
4213 mz_zip_array m_sorted_central_dir_offsets;
4214 MZ_FILE *m_pFile;

4220#define MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(array_ptr, element_size) \
4221 (array_ptr)->m_element_size = element_size
4222#define MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(array_ptr, element_type, index) \
4223 ((element_type *)((array_ptr)->m_p))[index]

4225static MZ_FORCEINLINE void mz_zip_array_clear(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4226 mz_zip_array *pArray) {
4227 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pArray->m_p);
4228 memset(pArray, 0, sizeof(mz_zip_array));
4229}
4230
4231static mz_bool mz_zip_array_ensure_capacity(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4232 mz_zip_array *pArray,
4233 size_t min_new_capacity,
4234 mz_uint growing) {
4235 void *pNew_p;
4236 size_t new_capacity = min_new_capacity;
4237 MZ_ASSERT(pArray->m_element_size);
4238 if (pArray->m_capacity >= min_new_capacity)
4239 return MZ_TRUE;
4240 if (growing) {
4241 new_capacity = MZ_MAX(1, pArray->m_capacity);
4242 while (new_capacity < min_new_capacity)
4243 new_capacity *= 2;
4244 }
4245 if (NULL == (pNew_p = pZip->m_pRealloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pArray->m_p,
4246 pArray->m_element_size, new_capacity)))
4247 return MZ_FALSE;
4248 pArray->m_p = pNew_p;
4249 pArray->m_capacity = new_capacity;
4250 return MZ_TRUE;
4251}
4252
4253static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool mz_zip_array_reserve(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4254 mz_zip_array *pArray,
4255 size_t new_capacity,
4256 mz_uint growing) {
4257 if (new_capacity > pArray->m_capacity) {
4258 if (!mz_zip_array_ensure_capacity(pZip, pArray, new_capacity, growing))
4259 return MZ_FALSE;
4260 }
4261 return MZ_TRUE;
4262}
4263
4264static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool mz_zip_array_resize(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4265 mz_zip_array *pArray,
4266 size_t new_size,
4267 mz_uint growing) {
4268 if (new_size > pArray->m_capacity) {
4269 if (!mz_zip_array_ensure_capacity(pZip, pArray, new_size, growing))
4270 return MZ_FALSE;
4271 }
4272 pArray->m_size = new_size;
4273 return MZ_TRUE;
4274}
4275
4276static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool mz_zip_array_ensure_room(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4277 mz_zip_array *pArray,
4278 size_t n) {
4279 return mz_zip_array_reserve(pZip, pArray, pArray->m_size + n, MZ_TRUE);
4280}
4281
4282static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool mz_zip_array_push_back(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4283 mz_zip_array *pArray,
4284 const void *pElements,
4285 size_t n) {
4286 if (0 == n)
4287 return MZ_TRUE;
4288 if (!pElements)
4289 return MZ_FALSE;
4290
4291 size_t orig_size = pArray->m_size;
4292 if (!mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, pArray, orig_size + n, MZ_TRUE))
4293 return MZ_FALSE;
4294 memcpy((mz_uint8 *)pArray->m_p + orig_size * pArray->m_element_size,
4295 pElements, n * pArray->m_element_size);
4296 return MZ_TRUE;
4297}
4298
4299#ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME
4300static time_t mz_zip_dos_to_time_t(int dos_time, int dos_date) {
4301 struct tm tm;
4302 memset(&tm, 0, sizeof(tm));
4303 tm.tm_isdst = -1;
4304 tm.tm_year = ((dos_date >> 9) & 127) + 1980 - 1900;
4305 tm.tm_mon = ((dos_date >> 5) & 15) - 1;
4306 tm.tm_mday = dos_date & 31;
4307 tm.tm_hour = (dos_time >> 11) & 31;
4308 tm.tm_min = (dos_time >> 5) & 63;
4309 tm.tm_sec = (dos_time << 1) & 62;
4310 return mktime(&tm);
4311}
4312
4313#ifndef MINIZ_NO_ARCHIVE_WRITING_APIS
4314static void mz_zip_time_t_to_dos_time(time_t time, mz_uint16 *pDOS_time,
4315 mz_uint16 *pDOS_date) {
4316#ifdef _MSC_VER
4317 struct tm tm_struct;
4318 struct tm *tm = &tm_struct;
4319 errno_t err = localtime_s(tm, &time);
4320 if (err) {
4321 *pDOS_date = 0;
4322 *pDOS_time = 0;
4323 return;
4324 }
4325#else
4326 struct tm *tm = localtime(&time);
4327#endif /* #ifdef _MSC_VER */
4328
4329 *pDOS_time = (mz_uint16)(((tm->tm_hour) << 11) + ((tm->tm_min) << 5) +
4330 ((tm->tm_sec) >> 1));
4331 *pDOS_date = (mz_uint16)(((tm->tm_year + 1900 - 1980) << 9) +
4332 ((tm->tm_mon + 1) << 5) + tm->tm_mday);
4333}
4334#endif /* MINIZ_NO_ARCHIVE_WRITING_APIS */
4335
4336#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
4337#ifndef MINIZ_NO_ARCHIVE_WRITING_APIS
4338static mz_bool mz_zip_get_file_modified_time(const char *pFilename,
4339 time_t *pTime) {
4340 struct MZ_FILE_STAT_STRUCT file_stat;
4341
4342 /* On Linux with x86 glibc, this call will fail on large files (I think >=
4343 * 0x80000000 bytes) unless you compiled with _LARGEFILE64_SOURCE. Argh. */
4344 if (MZ_FILE_STAT(pFilename, &file_stat) != 0)
4345 return MZ_FALSE;
4346
4347 *pTime = file_stat.st_mtime;
4348
4349 return MZ_TRUE;
4350}
4351#endif /* #ifndef MINIZ_NO_ARCHIVE_WRITING_APIS*/
4352
4353static mz_bool mz_zip_set_file_times(const char *pFilename, time_t access_time,
4354 time_t modified_time) {
4355 struct utimbuf t;
4356
4357 memset(&t, 0, sizeof(t));
4358 t.actime = access_time;
4359 t.modtime = modified_time;
4360
4361 return !utime(pFilename, &t);
4362}
4363#endif /* #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO */
4364#endif /* #ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME */
4365
4366static mz_bool mz_zip_reader_init_internal(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4367 mz_uint32 flags) {
4368 (void)flags;
4369 if ((!pZip) || (pZip->m_pState) || (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_INVALID))
4370 return MZ_FALSE;
4371
4372 if (!pZip->m_pAlloc)
4373 pZip->m_pAlloc = def_alloc_func;
4374 if (!pZip->m_pFree)
4375 pZip->m_pFree = def_free_func;
4376 if (!pZip->m_pRealloc)
4377 pZip->m_pRealloc = def_realloc_func;
4378
4379 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_READING;
4380 pZip->m_archive_size = 0;
4381 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = 0;
4382 pZip->m_total_files = 0;
4383
4384 if (NULL == (pZip->m_pState = (mz_zip_internal_state *)pZip->m_pAlloc(
4385 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, sizeof(mz_zip_internal_state))))
4386 return MZ_FALSE;
4387 memset(pZip->m_pState, 0, sizeof(mz_zip_internal_state));
4388 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir,
4389 sizeof(mz_uint8));
4390 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets,
4391 sizeof(mz_uint32));
4392 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets,
4393 sizeof(mz_uint32));
4394 return MZ_TRUE;
4395}
4396
4397static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool
4398mz_zip_reader_filename_less(const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_array,
4399 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_offsets,
4400 mz_uint l_index, mz_uint r_index) {
4401 const mz_uint8 *pL = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4402 pCentral_dir_array, mz_uint8,
4403 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(pCentral_dir_offsets, mz_uint32,
4404 l_index)),
4405 *pE;
4406 const mz_uint8 *pR = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4407 pCentral_dir_array, mz_uint8,
4408 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(pCentral_dir_offsets, mz_uint32, r_index));
4409 mz_uint l_len = MZ_READ_LE16(pL + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS),
4410 r_len = MZ_READ_LE16(pR + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4411 mz_uint8 l = 0, r = 0;
4412 pL += MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
4413 pR += MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
4414 pE = pL + MZ_MIN(l_len, r_len);
4415 while (pL < pE) {
4416 if ((l = MZ_TOLOWER(*pL)) != (r = MZ_TOLOWER(*pR)))
4417 break;
4418 pL++;
4419 pR++;
4420 }
4421 return (pL == pE) ? (l_len < r_len) : (l < r);
4422}
4423
4424#define MZ_SWAP_UINT32(a, b) \
4425 do { \
4426 mz_uint32 t = a; \
4427 a = b; \
4428 b = t; \
4429 } \
4430 MZ_MACRO_END
4431
4432// Heap sort of lowercased filenames, used to help accelerate plain central
4433// directory searches by mz_zip_reader_locate_file(). (Could also use qsort(),
4434// but it could allocate memory.)
4435static void
4436mz_zip_reader_sort_central_dir_offsets_by_filename(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
4437 mz_zip_internal_state *pState = pZip->m_pState;
4438 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_offsets = &pState->m_central_dir_offsets;
4439 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir = &pState->m_central_dir;
4440 mz_uint32 *pIndices = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4441 &pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32, 0);
4442 const int size = pZip->m_total_files;
4443 int start = (size - 2) >> 1, end;
4444 while (start >= 0) {
4445 int child, root = start;
4446 for (;;) {
4447 if ((child = (root << 1) + 1) >= size)
4448 break;
4449 child +=
4450 (((child + 1) < size) &&
4451 (mz_zip_reader_filename_less(pCentral_dir, pCentral_dir_offsets,
4452 pIndices[child], pIndices[child + 1])));
4453 if (!mz_zip_reader_filename_less(pCentral_dir, pCentral_dir_offsets,
4454 pIndices[root], pIndices[child]))
4455 break;
4456 MZ_SWAP_UINT32(pIndices[root], pIndices[child]);
4457 root = child;
4458 }
4459 start--;
4460 }
4461
4462 end = size - 1;
4463 while (end > 0) {
4464 int child, root = 0;
4465 MZ_SWAP_UINT32(pIndices[end], pIndices[0]);
4466 for (;;) {
4467 if ((child = (root << 1) + 1) >= end)
4468 break;
4469 child +=
4470 (((child + 1) < end) &&
4471 mz_zip_reader_filename_less(pCentral_dir, pCentral_dir_offsets,
4472 pIndices[child], pIndices[child + 1]));
4473 if (!mz_zip_reader_filename_less(pCentral_dir, pCentral_dir_offsets,
4474 pIndices[root], pIndices[child]))
4475 break;
4476 MZ_SWAP_UINT32(pIndices[root], pIndices[child]);
4477 root = child;
4478 }
4479 end--;
4480 }
4481}
4482
4483static mz_bool mz_zip_reader_read_central_dir(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4484 mz_uint32 flags) {
4485 mz_uint cdir_size, num_this_disk, cdir_disk_index;
4486 mz_uint64 cdir_ofs;
4487 mz_int64 cur_file_ofs;
4488 const mz_uint8 *p;
4489 mz_uint32 buf_u32[4096 / sizeof(mz_uint32)];
4490 mz_uint8 *pBuf = (mz_uint8 *)buf_u32;
4491 mz_bool sort_central_dir =
4492 ((flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_DO_NOT_SORT_CENTRAL_DIRECTORY) == 0);
4493 // Basic sanity checks - reject files which are too small, and check the first
4494 // 4 bytes of the file to make sure a local header is there.
4495 if (pZip->m_archive_size < MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
4496 return MZ_FALSE;
4497 // Find the end of central directory record by scanning the file from the end
4498 // towards the beginning.
4499 cur_file_ofs =
4500 MZ_MAX((mz_int64)pZip->m_archive_size - (mz_int64)sizeof(buf_u32), 0);
4501 for (;;) {
4502 int i,
4503 n = (int)MZ_MIN(sizeof(buf_u32), pZip->m_archive_size - cur_file_ofs);
4504 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pBuf, n) != (mz_uint)n)
4505 return MZ_FALSE;
4506 for (i = n - 4; i >= 0; --i)
4507 if (MZ_READ_LE32(pBuf + i) == MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG)
4508 break;
4509 if (i >= 0) {
4510 cur_file_ofs += i;
4511 break;
4512 }
4513 if ((!cur_file_ofs) || ((pZip->m_archive_size - cur_file_ofs) >=
4514 (0xFFFF + MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)))
4515 return MZ_FALSE;
4516 cur_file_ofs = MZ_MAX(cur_file_ofs - (sizeof(buf_u32) - 3), 0);
4517 }
4518 // Read and verify the end of central directory record.
4519 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pBuf,
4520 MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) !=
4521 MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
4522 return MZ_FALSE;
4523 if ((MZ_READ_LE32(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_SIG_OFS) !=
4524 MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG) ||
4525 ((pZip->m_total_files =
4526 MZ_READ_LE16(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_TOTAL_ENTRIES_OFS)) !=
4527 MZ_READ_LE16(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_NUM_ENTRIES_ON_DISK_OFS)))
4528 return MZ_FALSE;
4529
4530 num_this_disk = MZ_READ_LE16(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_NUM_THIS_DISK_OFS);
4531 cdir_disk_index = MZ_READ_LE16(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_NUM_DISK_CDIR_OFS);
4532 if (((num_this_disk | cdir_disk_index) != 0) &&
4533 ((num_this_disk != 1) || (cdir_disk_index != 1)))
4534 return MZ_FALSE;
4535
4536 if ((cdir_size = MZ_READ_LE32(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_SIZE_OFS)) <
4537 pZip->m_total_files * MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
4538 return MZ_FALSE;
4539
4540 cdir_ofs = MZ_READ_LE32(pBuf + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_OFS_OFS);
4541 if ((cdir_ofs + (mz_uint64)cdir_size) > pZip->m_archive_size)
4542 return MZ_FALSE;
4543
4544 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = cdir_ofs;
4545
4546 if (pZip->m_total_files) {
4547 mz_uint i, n;
4548
4549 // Read the entire central directory into a heap block, and allocate another
4550 // heap block to hold the unsorted central dir file record offsets, and
4551 // another to hold the sorted indices.
4552 if ((!mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir, cdir_size,
4553 MZ_FALSE)) ||
4554 (!mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets,
4555 pZip->m_total_files, MZ_FALSE)))
4556 return MZ_FALSE;
4557
4558 if (sort_central_dir) {
4559 if (!mz_zip_array_resize(pZip,
4560 &pZip->m_pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets,
4561 pZip->m_total_files, MZ_FALSE))
4562 return MZ_FALSE;
4563 }
4564
4565 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cdir_ofs,
4566 pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir.m_p,
4567 cdir_size) != cdir_size)
4568 return MZ_FALSE;
4569
4570 // Now create an index into the central directory file records, do some
4571 // basic sanity checking on each record, and check for zip64 entries (which
4572 // are not yet supported).
4573 p = (const mz_uint8 *)pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir.m_p;
4574 for (n = cdir_size, i = 0; i < pZip->m_total_files; ++i) {
4575 mz_uint total_header_size, comp_size, decomp_size, disk_index;
4576 if ((n < MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) ||
4577 (MZ_READ_LE32(p) != MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG))
4578 return MZ_FALSE;
4579 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32,
4580 i) =
4581 (mz_uint32)(p - (const mz_uint8 *)pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir.m_p);
4582 if (sort_central_dir)
4583 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(&pZip->m_pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets,
4584 mz_uint32, i) = i;
4585 comp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
4586 decomp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_DECOMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
4587 if (((!MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_METHOD_OFS)) &&
4588 (decomp_size != comp_size)) ||
4589 (decomp_size && !comp_size) || (decomp_size == 0xFFFFFFFF) ||
4590 (comp_size == 0xFFFFFFFF))
4591 return MZ_FALSE;
4592 disk_index = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_DISK_START_OFS);
4593 if ((disk_index != num_this_disk) && (disk_index != 1))
4594 return MZ_FALSE;
4595 if (((mz_uint64)MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_LOCAL_HEADER_OFS) +
4596 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + comp_size) > pZip->m_archive_size)
4597 return MZ_FALSE;
4598 if ((total_header_size = MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
4599 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
4600 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS) +
4601 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMMENT_LEN_OFS)) >
4602 n)
4603 return MZ_FALSE;
4604 n -= total_header_size;
4605 p += total_header_size;
4606 }
4607 }
4608
4609 if (sort_central_dir)
4610 mz_zip_reader_sort_central_dir_offsets_by_filename(pZip);
4611
4612 return MZ_TRUE;
4613}
4614
4615mz_bool mz_zip_reader_init(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint64 size,
4616 mz_uint32 flags) {
4617 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pRead))
4618 return MZ_FALSE;
4619 if (!mz_zip_reader_init_internal(pZip, flags))
4620 return MZ_FALSE;
4621 pZip->m_archive_size = size;
4622 if (!mz_zip_reader_read_central_dir(pZip, flags)) {
4623 mz_zip_reader_end(pZip);
4624 return MZ_FALSE;
4625 }
4626 return MZ_TRUE;
4627}
4628
4629static size_t mz_zip_mem_read_func(void *pOpaque, mz_uint64 file_ofs,
4630 void *pBuf, size_t n) {
4631 mz_zip_archive *pZip = (mz_zip_archive *)pOpaque;
4632 size_t s = (file_ofs >= pZip->m_archive_size)
4633 ? 0
4634 : (size_t)MZ_MIN(pZip->m_archive_size - file_ofs, n);
4635 memcpy(pBuf, (const mz_uint8 *)pZip->m_pState->m_pMem + file_ofs, s);
4636 return s;
4637}
4638
4639mz_bool mz_zip_reader_init_mem(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const void *pMem,
4640 size_t size, mz_uint32 flags) {
4641 if (!mz_zip_reader_init_internal(pZip, flags))
4642 return MZ_FALSE;
4643 pZip->m_archive_size = size;
4644 pZip->m_pRead = mz_zip_mem_read_func;
4645 pZip->m_pIO_opaque = pZip;
4646#ifdef __cplusplus
4647 pZip->m_pState->m_pMem = const_cast<void *>(pMem);
4648#else
4649 pZip->m_pState->m_pMem = (void *)pMem;
4650#endif
4651 pZip->m_pState->m_mem_size = size;
4652 if (!mz_zip_reader_read_central_dir(pZip, flags)) {
4653 mz_zip_reader_end(pZip);
4654 return MZ_FALSE;
4655 }
4656 return MZ_TRUE;
4657}
4658
4659#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
4660static size_t mz_zip_file_read_func(void *pOpaque, mz_uint64 file_ofs,
4661 void *pBuf, size_t n) {
4662 mz_zip_archive *pZip = (mz_zip_archive *)pOpaque;
4663 mz_int64 cur_ofs = MZ_FTELL64(pZip->m_pState->m_pFile);
4664 if (((mz_int64)file_ofs < 0) ||
4665 (((cur_ofs != (mz_int64)file_ofs)) &&
4666 (MZ_FSEEK64(pZip->m_pState->m_pFile, (mz_int64)file_ofs, SEEK_SET))))
4667 return 0;
4668 return MZ_FREAD(pBuf, 1, n, pZip->m_pState->m_pFile);
4669}
4670
4671mz_bool mz_zip_reader_init_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pFilename,
4672 mz_uint32 flags) {
4673 mz_uint64 file_size;
4674 MZ_FILE *pFile = MZ_FOPEN(pFilename, "rb");
4675 if (!pFile)
4676 return MZ_FALSE;
4677 if (MZ_FSEEK64(pFile, 0, SEEK_END)) {
4678 MZ_FCLOSE(pFile);
4679 return MZ_FALSE;
4680 }
4681 file_size = MZ_FTELL64(pFile);
4682 if (!mz_zip_reader_init_internal(pZip, flags)) {
4683 MZ_FCLOSE(pFile);
4684 return MZ_FALSE;
4685 }
4686 pZip->m_pRead = mz_zip_file_read_func;
4687 pZip->m_pIO_opaque = pZip;
4688 pZip->m_pState->m_pFile = pFile;
4689 pZip->m_archive_size = file_size;
4690 if (!mz_zip_reader_read_central_dir(pZip, flags)) {
4691 mz_zip_reader_end(pZip);
4692 return MZ_FALSE;
4693 }
4694 return MZ_TRUE;
4695}
4696#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
4697
4698mz_uint mz_zip_reader_get_num_files(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
4699 return pZip ? pZip->m_total_files : 0;
4700}
4701
4702static MZ_FORCEINLINE const mz_uint8 *
4703mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index) {
4704 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (file_index >= pZip->m_total_files) ||
4705 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_READING))
4706 return NULL;
4707 return &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4708 &pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir, mz_uint8,
4709 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32,
4710 file_index));
4711}
4712
4713mz_bool mz_zip_reader_is_file_encrypted(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4714 mz_uint file_index) {
4715 mz_uint m_bit_flag;
4716 const mz_uint8 *p = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pZip, file_index);
4717 if (!p)
4718 return MZ_FALSE;
4719 m_bit_flag = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_BIT_FLAG_OFS);
4720 return (m_bit_flag & 1);
4721}
4722
4723mz_bool mz_zip_reader_is_file_a_directory(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4724 mz_uint file_index) {
4725 mz_uint filename_len, external_attr;
4726 const mz_uint8 *p = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pZip, file_index);
4727 if (!p)
4728 return MZ_FALSE;
4729
4730 // First see if the filename ends with a '/' character.
4731 filename_len = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4732 if (filename_len) {
4733 if (*(p + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + filename_len - 1) == '/')
4734 return MZ_TRUE;
4735 }
4736
4737 // Bugfix: This code was also checking if the internal attribute was non-zero,
4738 // which wasn't correct. Most/all zip writers (hopefully) set DOS
4739 // file/directory attributes in the low 16-bits, so check for the DOS
4740 // directory flag and ignore the source OS ID in the created by field.
4741 // FIXME: Remove this check? Is it necessary - we already check the filename.
4742 external_attr = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTERNAL_ATTR_OFS);
4743 if ((external_attr & 0x10) != 0)
4744 return MZ_TRUE;
4745
4746 return MZ_FALSE;
4747}
4748
4749mz_bool mz_zip_reader_file_stat(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index,
4750 mz_zip_archive_file_stat *pStat) {
4751 mz_uint n;
4752 const mz_uint8 *p = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pZip, file_index);
4753 if ((!p) || (!pStat))
4754 return MZ_FALSE;
4755
4756 // Unpack the central directory record.
4757 pStat->m_file_index = file_index;
4758 pStat->m_central_dir_ofs = MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4759 &pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32, file_index);
4760 pStat->m_version_made_by = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_VERSION_MADE_BY_OFS);
4761 pStat->m_version_needed = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_VERSION_NEEDED_OFS);
4762 pStat->m_bit_flag = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_BIT_FLAG_OFS);
4763 pStat->m_method = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_METHOD_OFS);
4764#ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME
4765 pStat->m_time =
4766 mz_zip_dos_to_time_t(MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILE_TIME_OFS),
4767 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILE_DATE_OFS));
4768#endif
4769 pStat->m_crc32 = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_CRC32_OFS);
4770 pStat->m_comp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
4771 pStat->m_uncomp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_DECOMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
4772 pStat->m_internal_attr = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_INTERNAL_ATTR_OFS);
4773 pStat->m_external_attr = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTERNAL_ATTR_OFS);
4774 pStat->m_local_header_ofs = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_LOCAL_HEADER_OFS);
4775
4776 // Copy as much of the filename and comment as possible.
4777 n = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4778 n = MZ_MIN(n, MZ_ZIP_MAX_ARCHIVE_FILENAME_SIZE - 1);
4779 memcpy(pStat->m_filename, p + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE, n);
4780 pStat->m_filename[n] = '\0';
4781
4782 n = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMMENT_LEN_OFS);
4783 n = MZ_MIN(n, MZ_ZIP_MAX_ARCHIVE_FILE_COMMENT_SIZE - 1);
4784 pStat->m_comment_size = n;
4785 memcpy(pStat->m_comment,
4786 p + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
4787 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
4788 MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS),
4789 n);
4790 pStat->m_comment[n] = '\0';
4791
4792 return MZ_TRUE;
4793}
4794
4795mz_uint mz_zip_reader_get_filename(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index,
4796 char *pFilename, mz_uint filename_buf_size) {
4797 mz_uint n;
4798 const mz_uint8 *p = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pZip, file_index);
4799 if (!p) {
4800 if (filename_buf_size)
4801 pFilename[0] = '\0';
4802 return 0;
4803 }
4804 n = MZ_READ_LE16(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4805 if (filename_buf_size) {
4806 n = MZ_MIN(n, filename_buf_size - 1);
4807 memcpy(pFilename, p + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE, n);
4808 pFilename[n] = '\0';
4809 }
4810 return n + 1;
4811}
4812
4813static MZ_FORCEINLINE mz_bool mz_zip_reader_string_equal(const char *pA,
4814 const char *pB,
4815 mz_uint len,
4816 mz_uint flags) {
4817 mz_uint i;
4818 if (flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_CASE_SENSITIVE)
4819 return 0 == memcmp(pA, pB, len);
4820 for (i = 0; i < len; ++i)
4821 if (MZ_TOLOWER(pA[i]) != MZ_TOLOWER(pB[i]))
4822 return MZ_FALSE;
4823 return MZ_TRUE;
4824}
4825
4826static MZ_FORCEINLINE int
4827mz_zip_reader_filename_compare(const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_array,
4828 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_offsets,
4829 mz_uint l_index, const char *pR, mz_uint r_len) {
4830 const mz_uint8 *pL = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4831 pCentral_dir_array, mz_uint8,
4832 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(pCentral_dir_offsets, mz_uint32,
4833 l_index)),
4834 *pE;
4835 mz_uint l_len = MZ_READ_LE16(pL + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4836 mz_uint8 l = 0, r = 0;
4837 pL += MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
4838 pE = pL + MZ_MIN(l_len, r_len);
4839 while (pL < pE) {
4840 if ((l = MZ_TOLOWER(*pL)) != (r = MZ_TOLOWER(*pR)))
4841 break;
4842 pL++;
4843 pR++;
4844 }
4845 return (pL == pE) ? (int)(l_len - r_len) : (l - r);
4846}
4847
4848static int mz_zip_reader_locate_file_binary_search(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4849 const char *pFilename) {
4850 mz_zip_internal_state *pState = pZip->m_pState;
4851 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir_offsets = &pState->m_central_dir_offsets;
4852 const mz_zip_array *pCentral_dir = &pState->m_central_dir;
4853 mz_uint32 *pIndices = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4854 &pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32, 0);
4855 const int size = pZip->m_total_files;
4856 const mz_uint filename_len = (mz_uint)strlen(pFilename);
4857 int l = 0, h = size - 1;
4858 while (l <= h) {
4859 int m = (l + h) >> 1, file_index = pIndices[m],
4860 comp =
4861 mz_zip_reader_filename_compare(pCentral_dir, pCentral_dir_offsets,
4862 file_index, pFilename, filename_len);
4863 if (!comp)
4864 return file_index;
4865 else if (comp < 0)
4866 l = m + 1;
4867 else
4868 h = m - 1;
4869 }
4870 return -1;
4871}
4872
4873int mz_zip_reader_locate_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pName,
4874 const char *pComment, mz_uint flags) {
4875 mz_uint file_index;
4876 size_t name_len, comment_len;
4877 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pName) ||
4878 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_READING))
4879 return -1;
4880 if (((flags & (MZ_ZIP_FLAG_IGNORE_PATH | MZ_ZIP_FLAG_CASE_SENSITIVE)) == 0) &&
4881 (!pComment) && (pZip->m_pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets.m_size))
4882 return mz_zip_reader_locate_file_binary_search(pZip, pName);
4883 name_len = strlen(pName);
4884 if (name_len > 0xFFFF)
4885 return -1;
4886 comment_len = pComment ? strlen(pComment) : 0;
4887 if (comment_len > 0xFFFF)
4888 return -1;
4889 for (file_index = 0; file_index < pZip->m_total_files; file_index++) {
4890 const mz_uint8 *pHeader = &MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(
4891 &pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir, mz_uint8,
4892 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_ELEMENT(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets, mz_uint32,
4893 file_index));
4894 mz_uint filename_len = MZ_READ_LE16(pHeader + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS);
4895 const char *pFilename =
4896 (const char *)pHeader + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
4897 if (filename_len < name_len)
4898 continue;
4899 if (comment_len) {
4900 mz_uint file_extra_len = MZ_READ_LE16(pHeader + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS),
4901 file_comment_len =
4902 MZ_READ_LE16(pHeader + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMMENT_LEN_OFS);
4903 const char *pFile_comment = pFilename + filename_len + file_extra_len;
4904 if ((file_comment_len != comment_len) ||
4905 (!mz_zip_reader_string_equal(pComment, pFile_comment,
4906 file_comment_len, flags)))
4907 continue;
4908 }
4909 if ((flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_IGNORE_PATH) && (filename_len)) {
4910 int ofs = filename_len - 1;
4911 do {
4912 if ((pFilename[ofs] == '/') || (pFilename[ofs] == '\\') ||
4913 (pFilename[ofs] == ':'))
4914 break;
4915 } while (--ofs >= 0);
4916 ofs++;
4917 pFilename += ofs;
4918 filename_len -= ofs;
4919 }
4920 if ((filename_len == name_len) &&
4921 (mz_zip_reader_string_equal(pName, pFilename, filename_len, flags)))
4922 return file_index;
4923 }
4924 return -1;
4925}
4926
4927mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_to_mem_no_alloc(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
4928 mz_uint file_index, void *pBuf,
4929 size_t buf_size, mz_uint flags,
4930 void *pUser_read_buf,
4931 size_t user_read_buf_size) {
4932 int status = TINFL_STATUS_DONE;
4933 mz_uint64 needed_size, cur_file_ofs, comp_remaining,
4934 out_buf_ofs = 0, read_buf_size, read_buf_ofs = 0, read_buf_avail;
4935 mz_zip_archive_file_stat file_stat;
4936 void *pRead_buf;
4937 mz_uint32
4938 local_header_u32[(MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + sizeof(mz_uint32) - 1) /
4939 sizeof(mz_uint32)];
4940 mz_uint8 *pLocal_header = (mz_uint8 *)local_header_u32;
4941 tinfl_decompressor inflator;
4942
4943 if ((buf_size) && (!pBuf))
4944 return MZ_FALSE;
4945
4946 if (!mz_zip_reader_file_stat(pZip, file_index, &file_stat))
4947 return MZ_FALSE;
4948
4949 // Empty file, or a directory (but not always a directory - I've seen odd zips
4950 // with directories that have compressed data which inflates to 0 bytes)
4951 if (!file_stat.m_comp_size)
4952 return MZ_TRUE;
4953
4954 // Entry is a subdirectory (I've seen old zips with dir entries which have
4955 // compressed deflate data which inflates to 0 bytes, but these entries claim
4956 // to uncompress to 512 bytes in the headers). I'm torn how to handle this
4957 // case - should it fail instead?
4958 if (mz_zip_reader_is_file_a_directory(pZip, file_index))
4959 return MZ_TRUE;
4960
4961 // Encryption and patch files are not supported.
4962 if (file_stat.m_bit_flag & (1 | 32))
4963 return MZ_FALSE;
4964
4965 // This function only supports stored and deflate.
4966 if ((!(flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)) && (file_stat.m_method != 0) &&
4967 (file_stat.m_method != MZ_DEFLATED))
4968 return MZ_FALSE;
4969
4970 // Ensure supplied output buffer is large enough.
4971 needed_size = (flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA) ? file_stat.m_comp_size
4972 : file_stat.m_uncomp_size;
4973 if (buf_size < needed_size)
4974 return MZ_FALSE;
4975
4976 // Read and parse the local directory entry.
4977 cur_file_ofs = file_stat.m_local_header_ofs;
4978 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pLocal_header,
4979 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) !=
4980 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
4981 return MZ_FALSE;
4982 if (MZ_READ_LE32(pLocal_header) != MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG)
4983 return MZ_FALSE;
4984
4985 cur_file_ofs += MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
4986 MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
4987 MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS);
