4988 if ((cur_file_ofs + file_stat.m_comp_size) > pZip->m_archive_size)
4989 return MZ_FALSE;
4990
4991 if ((flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA) || (!file_stat.m_method)) {
4992 // The file is stored or the caller has requested the compressed data.
4993 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pBuf,
4994 (size_t)needed_size) != needed_size)
4995 return MZ_FALSE;
4996 return ((flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA) != 0) ||
4997 (mz_crc32(MZ_CRC32_INIT, (const mz_uint8 *)pBuf,
4998 (size_t)file_stat.m_uncomp_size) == file_stat.m_crc32);
4999 }
5000
5001 // Decompress the file either directly from memory or from a file input
5002 // buffer.
5003 tinfl_init(&inflator);
5004
5005 if (pZip->m_pState->m_pMem) {
5006 // Read directly from the archive in memory.
5007 pRead_buf = (mz_uint8 *)pZip->m_pState->m_pMem + cur_file_ofs;
5008 read_buf_size = read_buf_avail = file_stat.m_comp_size;
5009 comp_remaining = 0;
5010 } else if (pUser_read_buf) {
5011 // Use a user provided read buffer.
5012 if (!user_read_buf_size)
5013 return MZ_FALSE;
5014 pRead_buf = (mz_uint8 *)pUser_read_buf;
5015 read_buf_size = user_read_buf_size;
5016 read_buf_avail = 0;
5017 comp_remaining = file_stat.m_comp_size;
5018 } else {
5019 // Temporarily allocate a read buffer.
5020 read_buf_size = MZ_MIN(file_stat.m_comp_size, MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE);
5021#ifdef _MSC_VER
5022 if (((0, sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) &&
5023 (read_buf_size > 0x7FFFFFFF))
5024#else
5025 if (((sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) && (read_buf_size > 0x7FFFFFFF))
5026#endif
5027 return MZ_FALSE;
5028 if (NULL == (pRead_buf = pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1,
5029 (size_t)read_buf_size)))
5030 return MZ_FALSE;
5031 read_buf_avail = 0;
5032 comp_remaining = file_stat.m_comp_size;
5033 }
5034
5035 do {
5036 size_t in_buf_size,
5037 out_buf_size = (size_t)(file_stat.m_uncomp_size - out_buf_ofs);
5038 if ((!read_buf_avail) && (!pZip->m_pState->m_pMem)) {
5039 read_buf_avail = MZ_MIN(read_buf_size, comp_remaining);
5040 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pRead_buf,
5041 (size_t)read_buf_avail) != read_buf_avail) {
5042 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5043 break;
5044 }
5045 cur_file_ofs += read_buf_avail;
5046 comp_remaining -= read_buf_avail;
5047 read_buf_ofs = 0;
5048 }
5049 in_buf_size = (size_t)read_buf_avail;
5050 status = tinfl_decompress(
5051 &inflator, (mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf + read_buf_ofs, &in_buf_size,
5052 (mz_uint8 *)pBuf, (mz_uint8 *)pBuf + out_buf_ofs, &out_buf_size,
5053 TINFL_FLAG_USING_NON_WRAPPING_OUTPUT_BUF |
5054 (comp_remaining ? TINFL_FLAG_HAS_MORE_INPUT : 0));
5055 read_buf_avail -= in_buf_size;
5056 read_buf_ofs += in_buf_size;
5057 out_buf_ofs += out_buf_size;
5058 } while (status == TINFL_STATUS_NEEDS_MORE_INPUT);
5059
5060 if (status == TINFL_STATUS_DONE) {
5061 // Make sure the entire file was decompressed, and check its CRC.
5062 if ((out_buf_ofs != file_stat.m_uncomp_size) ||
5063 (mz_crc32(MZ_CRC32_INIT, (const mz_uint8 *)pBuf,
5064 (size_t)file_stat.m_uncomp_size) != file_stat.m_crc32))
5065 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5066 }
5067
5068 if ((!pZip->m_pState->m_pMem) && (!pUser_read_buf))
5069 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
5070
5071 return status == TINFL_STATUS_DONE;
5072}
5073
5074mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_mem_no_alloc(
5075 mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pFilename, void *pBuf, size_t buf_size,
5076 mz_uint flags, void *pUser_read_buf, size_t user_read_buf_size) {
5077 int file_index = mz_zip_reader_locate_file(pZip, pFilename, NULL, flags);
5078 if (file_index < 0)
5079 return MZ_FALSE;
5080 return mz_zip_reader_extract_to_mem_no_alloc(pZip, file_index, pBuf, buf_size,
5081 flags, pUser_read_buf,
5082 user_read_buf_size);
5083}
5084
5085mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_to_mem(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index,
5086 void *pBuf, size_t buf_size,
5087 mz_uint flags) {
5088 return mz_zip_reader_extract_to_mem_no_alloc(pZip, file_index, pBuf, buf_size,
5089 flags, NULL, 0);
5090}
5091
5092mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_mem(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5093 const char *pFilename, void *pBuf,
5094 size_t buf_size, mz_uint flags) {
5095 return mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_mem_no_alloc(pZip, pFilename, pBuf,
5096 buf_size, flags, NULL, 0);
5097}
5098
5099void *mz_zip_reader_extract_to_heap(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index,
5100 size_t *pSize, mz_uint flags) {
5101 mz_uint64 comp_size, uncomp_size, alloc_size;
5102 const mz_uint8 *p = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pZip, file_index);
5103 void *pBuf;
5104
5105 if (pSize)
5106 *pSize = 0;
5107 if (!p)
5108 return NULL;
5109
5110 comp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
5111 uncomp_size = MZ_READ_LE32(p + MZ_ZIP_CDH_DECOMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
5112
5113 alloc_size = (flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA) ? comp_size : uncomp_size;
5114#ifdef _MSC_VER
5115 if (((0, sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) && (alloc_size > 0x7FFFFFFF))
5116#else
5117 if (((sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) && (alloc_size > 0x7FFFFFFF))
5118#endif
5119 return NULL;
5120 if (NULL ==
5121 (pBuf = pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, (size_t)alloc_size)))
5122 return NULL;
5123
5124 if (!mz_zip_reader_extract_to_mem(pZip, file_index, pBuf, (size_t)alloc_size,
5125 flags)) {
5126 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
5127 return NULL;
5128 }
5129
5130 if (pSize)
5131 *pSize = (size_t)alloc_size;
5132 return pBuf;
5133}
5134
5135void *mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_heap(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5136 const char *pFilename, size_t *pSize,
5137 mz_uint flags) {
5138 int file_index = mz_zip_reader_locate_file(pZip, pFilename, NULL, flags);
5139 if (file_index < 0) {
5140 if (pSize)
5141 *pSize = 0;
5142 return MZ_FALSE;
5143 }
5144 return mz_zip_reader_extract_to_heap(pZip, file_index, pSize, flags);
5145}
5146
5147mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_to_callback(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5148 mz_uint file_index,
5149 mz_file_write_func pCallback,
5150 void *pOpaque, mz_uint flags) {
5151 int status = TINFL_STATUS_DONE;
5152 mz_uint file_crc32 = MZ_CRC32_INIT;
5153 mz_uint64 read_buf_size, read_buf_ofs = 0, read_buf_avail, comp_remaining,
5154 out_buf_ofs = 0, cur_file_ofs;
5155 mz_zip_archive_file_stat file_stat;
5156 void *pRead_buf = NULL;
5157 void *pWrite_buf = NULL;
5158 mz_uint32
5159 local_header_u32[(MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + sizeof(mz_uint32) - 1) /
5160 sizeof(mz_uint32)];
5161 mz_uint8 *pLocal_header = (mz_uint8 *)local_header_u32;
5162
5163 if (!mz_zip_reader_file_stat(pZip, file_index, &file_stat))
5164 return MZ_FALSE;
5165
5166 // Empty file, or a directory (but not always a directory - I've seen odd zips
5167 // with directories that have compressed data which inflates to 0 bytes)
5168 if (!file_stat.m_comp_size)
5169 return MZ_TRUE;
5170
5171 // Entry is a subdirectory (I've seen old zips with dir entries which have
5172 // compressed deflate data which inflates to 0 bytes, but these entries claim
5173 // to uncompress to 512 bytes in the headers). I'm torn how to handle this
5174 // case - should it fail instead?
5175 if (mz_zip_reader_is_file_a_directory(pZip, file_index))
5176 return MZ_TRUE;
5177
5178 // Encryption and patch files are not supported.
5179 if (file_stat.m_bit_flag & (1 | 32))
5180 return MZ_FALSE;
5181
5182 // This function only supports stored and deflate.
5183 if ((!(flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)) && (file_stat.m_method != 0) &&
5184 (file_stat.m_method != MZ_DEFLATED))
5185 return MZ_FALSE;
5186
5187 // Read and parse the local directory entry.
5188 cur_file_ofs = file_stat.m_local_header_ofs;
5189 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pLocal_header,
5190 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) !=
5191 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
5192 return MZ_FALSE;
5193 if (MZ_READ_LE32(pLocal_header) != MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG)
5194 return MZ_FALSE;
5195
5196 cur_file_ofs += MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
5197 MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
5198 MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS);
5199 if ((cur_file_ofs + file_stat.m_comp_size) > pZip->m_archive_size)
5200 return MZ_FALSE;
5201
5202 // Decompress the file either directly from memory or from a file input
5203 // buffer.
5204 if (pZip->m_pState->m_pMem) {
5205 pRead_buf = (mz_uint8 *)pZip->m_pState->m_pMem + cur_file_ofs;
5206 read_buf_size = read_buf_avail = file_stat.m_comp_size;
5207 comp_remaining = 0;
5208 } else {
5209 read_buf_size = MZ_MIN(file_stat.m_comp_size, MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE);
5210 if (NULL == (pRead_buf = pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1,
5211 (size_t)read_buf_size)))
5212 return MZ_FALSE;
5213 read_buf_avail = 0;
5214 comp_remaining = file_stat.m_comp_size;
5215 }
5216
5217 if ((flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA) || (!file_stat.m_method)) {
5218 // The file is stored or the caller has requested the compressed data.
5219 if (pZip->m_pState->m_pMem) {
5220#ifdef _MSC_VER
5221 if (((0, sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) &&
5222 (file_stat.m_comp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5223#else
5224 if (((sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32))) &&
5225 (file_stat.m_comp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5226#endif
5227 return MZ_FALSE;
5228 if (pCallback(pOpaque, out_buf_ofs, pRead_buf,
5229 (size_t)file_stat.m_comp_size) != file_stat.m_comp_size)
5230 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5231 else if (!(flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA))
5232 file_crc32 =
5233 (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(file_crc32, (const mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf,
5234 (size_t)file_stat.m_comp_size);
5235 // cur_file_ofs += file_stat.m_comp_size;
5236 out_buf_ofs += file_stat.m_comp_size;
5237 // comp_remaining = 0;
5238 } else {
5239 while (comp_remaining) {
5240 read_buf_avail = MZ_MIN(read_buf_size, comp_remaining);
5241 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pRead_buf,
5242 (size_t)read_buf_avail) != read_buf_avail) {
5243 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5244 break;
5245 }
5246
5247 if (!(flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA))
5248 file_crc32 = (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(
5249 file_crc32, (const mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf, (size_t)read_buf_avail);
5250
5251 if (pCallback(pOpaque, out_buf_ofs, pRead_buf,
5252 (size_t)read_buf_avail) != read_buf_avail) {
5253 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5254 break;
5255 }
5256 cur_file_ofs += read_buf_avail;
5257 out_buf_ofs += read_buf_avail;
5258 comp_remaining -= read_buf_avail;
5259 }
5260 }
5261 } else {
5262 tinfl_decompressor inflator;
5263 tinfl_init(&inflator);
5264
5265 if (NULL == (pWrite_buf = pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1,
5266 TINFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE)))
5267 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5268 else {
5269 do {
5270 mz_uint8 *pWrite_buf_cur =
5271 (mz_uint8 *)pWrite_buf + (out_buf_ofs & (TINFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - 1));
5272 size_t in_buf_size,
5273 out_buf_size =
5274 TINFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - (out_buf_ofs & (TINFL_LZ_DICT_SIZE - 1));
5275 if ((!read_buf_avail) && (!pZip->m_pState->m_pMem)) {
5276 read_buf_avail = MZ_MIN(read_buf_size, comp_remaining);
5277 if (pZip->m_pRead(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, pRead_buf,
5278 (size_t)read_buf_avail) != read_buf_avail) {
5279 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5280 break;
5281 }
5282 cur_file_ofs += read_buf_avail;
5283 comp_remaining -= read_buf_avail;
5284 read_buf_ofs = 0;
5285 }
5286
5287 in_buf_size = (size_t)read_buf_avail;
5288 status = tinfl_decompress(
5289 &inflator, (const mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf + read_buf_ofs, &in_buf_size,
5290 (mz_uint8 *)pWrite_buf, pWrite_buf_cur, &out_buf_size,
5291 comp_remaining ? TINFL_FLAG_HAS_MORE_INPUT : 0);
5292 read_buf_avail -= in_buf_size;
5293 read_buf_ofs += in_buf_size;
5294
5295 if (out_buf_size) {
5296 if (pCallback(pOpaque, out_buf_ofs, pWrite_buf_cur, out_buf_size) !=
5297 out_buf_size) {
5298 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5299 break;
5300 }
5301 file_crc32 =
5302 (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(file_crc32, pWrite_buf_cur, out_buf_size);
5303 if ((out_buf_ofs += out_buf_size) > file_stat.m_uncomp_size) {
5304 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5305 break;
5306 }
5307 }
5308 } while ((status == TINFL_STATUS_NEEDS_MORE_INPUT) ||
5309 (status == TINFL_STATUS_HAS_MORE_OUTPUT));
5310 }
5311 }
5312
5313 if ((status == TINFL_STATUS_DONE) &&
5314 (!(flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA))) {
5315 // Make sure the entire file was decompressed, and check its CRC.
5316 if ((out_buf_ofs != file_stat.m_uncomp_size) ||
5317 (file_crc32 != file_stat.m_crc32))
5318 status = TINFL_STATUS_FAILED;
5319 }
5320
5321 if (!pZip->m_pState->m_pMem)
5322 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
5323 if (pWrite_buf)
5324 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pWrite_buf);
5325
5326 return status == TINFL_STATUS_DONE;
5327}
5328
5329mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_callback(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5330 const char *pFilename,
5331 mz_file_write_func pCallback,
5332 void *pOpaque, mz_uint flags) {
5333 int file_index = mz_zip_reader_locate_file(pZip, pFilename, NULL, flags);
5334 if (file_index < 0)
5335 return MZ_FALSE;
5336 return mz_zip_reader_extract_to_callback(pZip, file_index, pCallback, pOpaque,
5337 flags);
5338}
5339
5340#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5341static size_t mz_zip_file_write_callback(void *pOpaque, mz_uint64 ofs,
5342 const void *pBuf, size_t n) {
5343 (void)ofs;
5344 return MZ_FWRITE(pBuf, 1, n, (MZ_FILE *)pOpaque);
5345}
5346
5347mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_to_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint file_index,
5348 const char *pDst_filename,
5349 mz_uint flags) {
5350 mz_bool status;
5351 mz_zip_archive_file_stat file_stat;
5352 MZ_FILE *pFile;
5353 if (!mz_zip_reader_file_stat(pZip, file_index, &file_stat))
5354 return MZ_FALSE;
5355
5356 pFile = MZ_FOPEN(pDst_filename, "wb");
5357 if (!pFile)
5358 return MZ_FALSE;
5359 status = mz_zip_reader_extract_to_callback(
5360 pZip, file_index, mz_zip_file_write_callback, pFile, flags);
5361 if (MZ_FCLOSE(pFile) == EOF)
5362 return MZ_FALSE;
5363#ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME
5364 if (status) {
5365 mz_zip_set_file_times(pDst_filename, file_stat.m_time, file_stat.m_time);
5366 }
5367#endif
5368
5369 return status;
5370}
5371#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5372
5373mz_bool mz_zip_reader_end(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
5374 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pZip->m_pAlloc) || (!pZip->m_pFree) ||
5375 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_READING))
5376 return MZ_FALSE;
5377
5378 mz_zip_internal_state *pState = pZip->m_pState;
5379 pZip->m_pState = NULL;
5380 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir);
5381 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets);
5382 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets);
5383
5384#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5385 if (pState->m_pFile) {
5386 MZ_FCLOSE(pState->m_pFile);
5387 pState->m_pFile = NULL;
5388 }
5389#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5390
5391 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pState);
5392
5393 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_INVALID;
5394
5395 return MZ_TRUE;
5396}
5397
5398#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5399mz_bool mz_zip_reader_extract_file_to_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5400 const char *pArchive_filename,
5401 const char *pDst_filename,
5402 mz_uint flags) {
5403 int file_index =
5404 mz_zip_reader_locate_file(pZip, pArchive_filename, NULL, flags);
5405 if (file_index < 0)
5406 return MZ_FALSE;
5407 return mz_zip_reader_extract_to_file(pZip, file_index, pDst_filename, flags);
5408}
5409#endif
5410
5411// ------------------- .ZIP archive writing
5412
5413#ifndef MINIZ_NO_ARCHIVE_WRITING_APIS
5414
5415static void mz_write_le16(mz_uint8 *p, mz_uint16 v) {
5416 p[0] = (mz_uint8)v;
5417 p[1] = (mz_uint8)(v >> 8);
5418}
5419static void mz_write_le32(mz_uint8 *p, mz_uint32 v) {
5420 p[0] = (mz_uint8)v;
5421 p[1] = (mz_uint8)(v >> 8);
5422 p[2] = (mz_uint8)(v >> 16);
5423 p[3] = (mz_uint8)(v >> 24);
5424}
5425#define MZ_WRITE_LE16(p, v) mz_write_le16((mz_uint8 *)(p), (mz_uint16)(v))
5426#define MZ_WRITE_LE32(p, v) mz_write_le32((mz_uint8 *)(p), (mz_uint32)(v))
5427
5428mz_bool mz_zip_writer_init(mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint64 existing_size) {
5429 if ((!pZip) || (pZip->m_pState) || (!pZip->m_pWrite) ||
5430 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_INVALID))
5431 return MZ_FALSE;
5432
5433 if (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment) {
5434 // Ensure user specified file offset alignment is a power of 2.
5435 if (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1))
5436 return MZ_FALSE;
5437 }
5438
5439 if (!pZip->m_pAlloc)
5440 pZip->m_pAlloc = def_alloc_func;
5441 if (!pZip->m_pFree)
5442 pZip->m_pFree = def_free_func;
5443 if (!pZip->m_pRealloc)
5444 pZip->m_pRealloc = def_realloc_func;
5445
5446 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING;
5447 pZip->m_archive_size = existing_size;
5448 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = 0;
5449 pZip->m_total_files = 0;
5450
5451 if (NULL == (pZip->m_pState = (mz_zip_internal_state *)pZip->m_pAlloc(
5452 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, sizeof(mz_zip_internal_state))))
5453 return MZ_FALSE;
5454 memset(pZip->m_pState, 0, sizeof(mz_zip_internal_state));
5455 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir,
5456 sizeof(mz_uint8));
5457 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_central_dir_offsets,
5458 sizeof(mz_uint32));
5459 MZ_ZIP_ARRAY_SET_ELEMENT_SIZE(&pZip->m_pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets,
5460 sizeof(mz_uint32));
5461 return MZ_TRUE;
5462}
5463
5464static size_t mz_zip_heap_write_func(void *pOpaque, mz_uint64 file_ofs,
5465 const void *pBuf, size_t n) {
5466 mz_zip_archive *pZip = (mz_zip_archive *)pOpaque;
5467 mz_zip_internal_state *pState = pZip->m_pState;
5468 mz_uint64 new_size = MZ_MAX(file_ofs + n, pState->m_mem_size);
5469
5470 if ((!n) ||
5471 ((sizeof(size_t) == sizeof(mz_uint32)) && (new_size > 0x7FFFFFFF)))
5472 return 0;
5473
5474 if (new_size > pState->m_mem_capacity) {
5475 void *pNew_block;
5476 size_t new_capacity = MZ_MAX(64, pState->m_mem_capacity);
5477 while (new_capacity < new_size)
5478 new_capacity *= 2;
5479 if (NULL == (pNew_block = pZip->m_pRealloc(
5480 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pState->m_pMem, 1, new_capacity)))
5481 return 0;
5482 pState->m_pMem = pNew_block;
5483 pState->m_mem_capacity = new_capacity;
5484 }
5485 memcpy((mz_uint8 *)pState->m_pMem + file_ofs, pBuf, n);
5486 pState->m_mem_size = (size_t)new_size;
5487 return n;
5488}
5489
5490mz_bool mz_zip_writer_init_heap(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5491 size_t size_to_reserve_at_beginning,
5492 size_t initial_allocation_size) {
5493 pZip->m_pWrite = mz_zip_heap_write_func;
5494 pZip->m_pIO_opaque = pZip;
5495 if (!mz_zip_writer_init(pZip, size_to_reserve_at_beginning))
5496 return MZ_FALSE;
5497 if (0 != (initial_allocation_size = MZ_MAX(initial_allocation_size,
5498 size_to_reserve_at_beginning))) {
5499 if (NULL == (pZip->m_pState->m_pMem = pZip->m_pAlloc(
5500 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, initial_allocation_size))) {
5501 mz_zip_writer_end(pZip);
5502 return MZ_FALSE;
5503 }
5504 pZip->m_pState->m_mem_capacity = initial_allocation_size;
5505 }
5506 return MZ_TRUE;
5507}
5508
5509#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5510static size_t mz_zip_file_write_func(void *pOpaque, mz_uint64 file_ofs,
5511 const void *pBuf, size_t n) {
5512 mz_zip_archive *pZip = (mz_zip_archive *)pOpaque;
5513 mz_int64 cur_ofs = MZ_FTELL64(pZip->m_pState->m_pFile);
5514 if (((mz_int64)file_ofs < 0) ||
5515 (((cur_ofs != (mz_int64)file_ofs)) &&
5516 (MZ_FSEEK64(pZip->m_pState->m_pFile, (mz_int64)file_ofs, SEEK_SET))))
5517 return 0;
5518 return MZ_FWRITE(pBuf, 1, n, pZip->m_pState->m_pFile);
5519}
5520
5521mz_bool mz_zip_writer_init_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pFilename,
5522 mz_uint64 size_to_reserve_at_beginning) {
5523 MZ_FILE *pFile;
5524 pZip->m_pWrite = mz_zip_file_write_func;
5525 pZip->m_pIO_opaque = pZip;
5526 if (!mz_zip_writer_init(pZip, size_to_reserve_at_beginning))
5527 return MZ_FALSE;
5528 if (NULL == (pFile = MZ_FOPEN(pFilename, "wb"))) {
5529 mz_zip_writer_end(pZip);
5530 return MZ_FALSE;
5531 }
5532 pZip->m_pState->m_pFile = pFile;
5533 if (size_to_reserve_at_beginning) {
5534 mz_uint64 cur_ofs = 0;
5535 char buf[4096];
5536 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(buf);
5537 do {
5538 size_t n = (size_t)MZ_MIN(sizeof(buf), size_to_reserve_at_beginning);
5539 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_ofs, buf, n) != n) {
5540 mz_zip_writer_end(pZip);
5541 return MZ_FALSE;
5542 }
5543 cur_ofs += n;
5544 size_to_reserve_at_beginning -= n;
5545 } while (size_to_reserve_at_beginning);
5546 }
5547 return MZ_TRUE;
5548}
5549#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5550
5551mz_bool mz_zip_writer_init_from_reader(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5552 const char *pFilename) {
5553 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
5554 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_READING))
5555 return MZ_FALSE;
5556 // No sense in trying to write to an archive that's already at the support max
5557 // size
5558 if ((pZip->m_total_files == 0xFFFF) ||
5559 ((pZip->m_archive_size + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
5560 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5561 return MZ_FALSE;
5562
5563 pState = pZip->m_pState;
5564
5565 if (pState->m_pFile) {
5566#ifdef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5567 pFilename;
5568 return MZ_FALSE;
5569#else
5570 // Archive is being read from stdio - try to reopen as writable.
5571 if (pZip->m_pIO_opaque != pZip)
5572 return MZ_FALSE;
5573 if (!pFilename)
5574 return MZ_FALSE;
5575 pZip->m_pWrite = mz_zip_file_write_func;
5576 if (NULL ==
5577 (pState->m_pFile = MZ_FREOPEN(pFilename, "r+b", pState->m_pFile))) {
5578 // The mz_zip_archive is now in a bogus state because pState->m_pFile is
5579 // NULL, so just close it.
5580 mz_zip_reader_end(pZip);
5581 return MZ_FALSE;
5582 }
5583#endif // #ifdef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5584 } else if (pState->m_pMem) {
5585 // Archive lives in a memory block. Assume it's from the heap that we can
5586 // resize using the realloc callback.
5587 if (pZip->m_pIO_opaque != pZip)
5588 return MZ_FALSE;
5589 pState->m_mem_capacity = pState->m_mem_size;
5590 pZip->m_pWrite = mz_zip_heap_write_func;
5591 }
5592 // Archive is being read via a user provided read function - make sure the
5593 // user has specified a write function too.
5594 else if (!pZip->m_pWrite)
5595 return MZ_FALSE;
5596
5597 // Start writing new files at the archive's current central directory
5598 // location.
5599 pZip->m_archive_size = pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs;
5600 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING;
5601 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = 0;
5602
5603 return MZ_TRUE;
5604}
5605
5606mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_mem(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pArchive_name,
5607 const void *pBuf, size_t buf_size,
5608 mz_uint level_and_flags) {
5609 return mz_zip_writer_add_mem_ex(pZip, pArchive_name, pBuf, buf_size, NULL, 0,
5610 level_and_flags, 0, 0);
5611}
5612
5613typedef struct {
5614 mz_zip_archive *m_pZip;
5615 mz_uint64 m_cur_archive_file_ofs;
5616 mz_uint64 m_comp_size;
5617} mz_zip_writer_add_state;
5618
5619static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_put_buf_callback(const void *pBuf, int len,
5620 void *pUser) {
5621 mz_zip_writer_add_state *pState = (mz_zip_writer_add_state *)pUser;
5622 if ((int)pState->m_pZip->m_pWrite(pState->m_pZip->m_pIO_opaque,
5623 pState->m_cur_archive_file_ofs, pBuf,
5624 len) != len)
5625 return MZ_FALSE;
5626 pState->m_cur_archive_file_ofs += len;
5627 pState->m_comp_size += len;
5628 return MZ_TRUE;
5629}
5630
5631static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_create_local_dir_header(
5632 mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint8 *pDst, mz_uint16 filename_size,
5633 mz_uint16 extra_size, mz_uint64 uncomp_size, mz_uint64 comp_size,
5634 mz_uint32 uncomp_crc32, mz_uint16 method, mz_uint16 bit_flags,
5635 mz_uint16 dos_time, mz_uint16 dos_date) {
5636 (void)pZip;
5637 memset(pDst, 0, MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE);
5638 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_SIG_OFS, MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG);
5639 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_VERSION_NEEDED_OFS, method ? 20 : 0);
5640 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_BIT_FLAG_OFS, bit_flags);
5641 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_METHOD_OFS, method);
5642 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILE_TIME_OFS, dos_time);
5643 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILE_DATE_OFS, dos_date);
5644 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_CRC32_OFS, uncomp_crc32);
5645 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS, comp_size);
5646 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_DECOMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS, uncomp_size);
5647 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS, filename_size);
5648 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS, extra_size);
5649 return MZ_TRUE;
5650}
5651
5652static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_create_central_dir_header(
5653 mz_zip_archive *pZip, mz_uint8 *pDst, mz_uint16 filename_size,
5654 mz_uint16 extra_size, mz_uint16 comment_size, mz_uint64 uncomp_size,
5655 mz_uint64 comp_size, mz_uint32 uncomp_crc32, mz_uint16 method,
5656 mz_uint16 bit_flags, mz_uint16 dos_time, mz_uint16 dos_date,
5657 mz_uint64 local_header_ofs, mz_uint32 ext_attributes) {
5658 (void)pZip;
5659 mz_uint16 version_made_by = 10 * MZ_VER_MAJOR + MZ_VER_MINOR;
5660 version_made_by |= (MZ_PLATFORM << 8);
5661
5662 memset(pDst, 0, MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE);
5663 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_SIG_OFS, MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG);
5664 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_VERSION_MADE_BY_OFS, version_made_by);
5665 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_VERSION_NEEDED_OFS, method ? 20 : 0);
5666 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_BIT_FLAG_OFS, bit_flags);
5667 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_METHOD_OFS, method);
5668 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILE_TIME_OFS, dos_time);
5669 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILE_DATE_OFS, dos_date);
5670 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_CRC32_OFS, uncomp_crc32);
5671 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS, comp_size);
5672 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_DECOMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS, uncomp_size);
5673 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS, filename_size);
5674 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS, extra_size);
5675 MZ_WRITE_LE16(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMMENT_LEN_OFS, comment_size);
5676 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTERNAL_ATTR_OFS, ext_attributes);
5677 MZ_WRITE_LE32(pDst + MZ_ZIP_CDH_LOCAL_HEADER_OFS, local_header_ofs);
5678 return MZ_TRUE;
5679}
5680
5681static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_to_central_dir(
5682 mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pFilename, mz_uint16 filename_size,
5683 const void *pExtra, mz_uint16 extra_size, const void *pComment,
5684 mz_uint16 comment_size, mz_uint64 uncomp_size, mz_uint64 comp_size,
5685 mz_uint32 uncomp_crc32, mz_uint16 method, mz_uint16 bit_flags,
5686 mz_uint16 dos_time, mz_uint16 dos_date, mz_uint64 local_header_ofs,
5687 mz_uint32 ext_attributes) {
5688 mz_zip_internal_state *pState = pZip->m_pState;
5689 mz_uint32 central_dir_ofs = (mz_uint32)pState->m_central_dir.m_size;
5690 size_t orig_central_dir_size = pState->m_central_dir.m_size;
5691 mz_uint8 central_dir_header[MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
5692
5693 // No zip64 support yet
5694 if ((local_header_ofs > 0xFFFFFFFF) ||
5695 (((mz_uint64)pState->m_central_dir.m_size +
5696 MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + filename_size + extra_size +
5697 comment_size) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5698 return MZ_FALSE;
5699
5700 if (!mz_zip_writer_create_central_dir_header(
5701 pZip, central_dir_header, filename_size, extra_size, comment_size,
5702 uncomp_size, comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, bit_flags, dos_time,
5703 dos_date, local_header_ofs, ext_attributes))
5704 return MZ_FALSE;
5705
5706 if ((!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, central_dir_header,
5707 MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)) ||
5708 (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, pFilename,
5709 filename_size)) ||
5710 (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, pExtra,
5711 extra_size)) ||
5712 (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, pComment,
5713 comment_size)) ||
5714 (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets,
5715 &central_dir_ofs, 1))) {
5716 // Try to push the central directory array back into its original state.
5717 mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, orig_central_dir_size,
5718 MZ_FALSE);
5719 return MZ_FALSE;
5720 }
5721
5722 return MZ_TRUE;
5723}
5724
5725static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_validate_archive_name(const char *pArchive_name) {
5726 // Basic ZIP archive filename validity checks: Valid filenames cannot start
5727 // with a forward slash, cannot contain a drive letter, and cannot use
5728 // DOS-style backward slashes.
5729 if (*pArchive_name == '/')
5730 return MZ_FALSE;
5731 while (*pArchive_name) {
5732 if ((*pArchive_name == '\\') || (*pArchive_name == ':'))
5733 return MZ_FALSE;
5734 pArchive_name++;
5735 }
5736 return MZ_TRUE;
5737}
5738
5739static mz_uint
5740mz_zip_writer_compute_padding_needed_for_file_alignment(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
5741 mz_uint32 n;
5742 if (!pZip->m_file_offset_alignment)
5743 return 0;
5744 n = (mz_uint32)(pZip->m_archive_size & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1));
5745 return (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - n) &
5746 (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1);
5747}
5748
5749static mz_bool mz_zip_writer_write_zeros(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5750 mz_uint64 cur_file_ofs, mz_uint32 n) {
5751 char buf[4096];
5752 memset(buf, 0, MZ_MIN(sizeof(buf), n));
5753 while (n) {
5754 mz_uint32 s = MZ_MIN(sizeof(buf), n);
5755 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_file_ofs, buf, s) != s)
5756 return MZ_FALSE;
5757 cur_file_ofs += s;
5758 n -= s;
5759 }
5760 return MZ_TRUE;
5761}
5762
5763mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_mem_ex(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
5764 const char *pArchive_name, const void *pBuf,
5765 size_t buf_size, const void *pComment,
5766 mz_uint16 comment_size,
5767 mz_uint level_and_flags, mz_uint64 uncomp_size,
5768 mz_uint32 uncomp_crc32) {
5769 mz_uint32 ext_attributes = 0;
5770 mz_uint16 method = 0, dos_time = 0, dos_date = 0;
5771 mz_uint level, num_alignment_padding_bytes;
5772 mz_uint64 local_dir_header_ofs, cur_archive_file_ofs, comp_size = 0;
5773 size_t archive_name_size;
5774 mz_uint8 local_dir_header[MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
5775 tdefl_compressor *pComp = NULL;
5776 mz_bool store_data_uncompressed;
5777 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
5778
5779 if ((int)level_and_flags < 0)
5780 level_and_flags = MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL;
5781 level = level_and_flags & 0xF;
5782 store_data_uncompressed =
5783 ((!level) || (level_and_flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA));
5784
5785 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) ||
5786 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING) || ((buf_size) && (!pBuf)) ||
5787 (!pArchive_name) || ((comment_size) && (!pComment)) ||
5788 (pZip->m_total_files == 0xFFFF) || (level > MZ_UBER_COMPRESSION))
5789 return MZ_FALSE;
5790
5791 local_dir_header_ofs = cur_archive_file_ofs = pZip->m_archive_size;
5792 pState = pZip->m_pState;
5793
5794 if ((!(level_and_flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)) && (uncomp_size))
5795 return MZ_FALSE;
5796 // No zip64 support yet
5797 if ((buf_size > 0xFFFFFFFF) || (uncomp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5798 return MZ_FALSE;
5799 if (!mz_zip_writer_validate_archive_name(pArchive_name))
5800 return MZ_FALSE;
5801
5802#ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME
5803 {
5804 time_t cur_time;
5805 time(&cur_time);
5806 mz_zip_time_t_to_dos_time(cur_time, &dos_time, &dos_date);
5807 }
5808#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_TIME
5809
5810 archive_name_size = strlen(pArchive_name);
5811 if (archive_name_size > 0xFFFF)
5812 return MZ_FALSE;
5813
5814 num_alignment_padding_bytes =
5815 mz_zip_writer_compute_padding_needed_for_file_alignment(pZip);
5816
5817 // no zip64 support yet
5818 if ((pZip->m_total_files == 0xFFFF) ||
5819 ((pZip->m_archive_size + num_alignment_padding_bytes +
5820 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
5821 comment_size + archive_name_size) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5822 return MZ_FALSE;
5823
5824 if ((archive_name_size) && (pArchive_name[archive_name_size - 1] == '/')) {
5825 // Set DOS Subdirectory attribute bit.
5826 ext_attributes |= 0x10;
5827 // Subdirectories cannot contain data.
5828 if ((buf_size) || (uncomp_size))
5829 return MZ_FALSE;
5830 }
5831
5832 // Try to do any allocations before writing to the archive, so if an
5833 // allocation fails the file remains unmodified. (A good idea if we're doing
5834 // an in-place modification.)
5835 if ((!mz_zip_array_ensure_room(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir,
5836 MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
5837 archive_name_size + comment_size)) ||
5838 (!mz_zip_array_ensure_room(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets, 1)))
5839 return MZ_FALSE;
5840
5841 if ((!store_data_uncompressed) && (buf_size)) {
5842 if (NULL == (pComp = (tdefl_compressor *)pZip->m_pAlloc(
5843 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, sizeof(tdefl_compressor))))
5844 return MZ_FALSE;
5845 }
5846
5847 if (!mz_zip_writer_write_zeros(pZip, cur_archive_file_ofs,
5848 num_alignment_padding_bytes +
5849 sizeof(local_dir_header))) {
5850 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
5851 return MZ_FALSE;
5852 }
5853 local_dir_header_ofs += num_alignment_padding_bytes;
5854 if (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment) {
5855 MZ_ASSERT((local_dir_header_ofs & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1)) ==
5856 0);
5857 }
5858 cur_archive_file_ofs +=
5859 num_alignment_padding_bytes + sizeof(local_dir_header);
5860
5861 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(local_dir_header);
5862 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_archive_file_ofs, pArchive_name,
5863 archive_name_size) != archive_name_size) {
5864 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
5865 return MZ_FALSE;
5866 }
5867 cur_archive_file_ofs += archive_name_size;
5868
5869 if (!(level_and_flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)) {
5870 uncomp_crc32 =
5871 (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(MZ_CRC32_INIT, (const mz_uint8 *)pBuf, buf_size);
5872 uncomp_size = buf_size;
5873 if (uncomp_size <= 3) {
5874 level = 0;
5875 store_data_uncompressed = MZ_TRUE;
5876 }
5877 }
5878
5879 if (store_data_uncompressed) {
5880 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_archive_file_ofs, pBuf,
5881 buf_size) != buf_size) {
5882 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
5883 return MZ_FALSE;
5884 }
5885
5886 cur_archive_file_ofs += buf_size;
5887 comp_size = buf_size;
5888
5889 if (level_and_flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)
5890 method = MZ_DEFLATED;
5891 } else if (buf_size) {
5892 mz_zip_writer_add_state state;
5893
5894 state.m_pZip = pZip;
5895 state.m_cur_archive_file_ofs = cur_archive_file_ofs;
5896 state.m_comp_size = 0;
5897
5898 if ((tdefl_init(pComp, mz_zip_writer_add_put_buf_callback, &state,
5899 tdefl_create_comp_flags_from_zip_params(
5900 level, -15, MZ_DEFAULT_STRATEGY)) !=
5901 TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY) ||
5902 (tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp, pBuf, buf_size, TDEFL_FINISH) !=
5903 TDEFL_STATUS_DONE)) {
5904 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
5905 return MZ_FALSE;
5906 }
5907
5908 comp_size = state.m_comp_size;
5909 cur_archive_file_ofs = state.m_cur_archive_file_ofs;
5910
5911 method = MZ_DEFLATED;
5912 }
5913
5914 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
5915 pComp = NULL;
5916
5917 // no zip64 support yet
5918 if ((comp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF) || (cur_archive_file_ofs > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5919 return MZ_FALSE;
5920
5921 if (!mz_zip_writer_create_local_dir_header(
5922 pZip, local_dir_header, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, 0, uncomp_size,
5923 comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0, dos_time, dos_date))
5924 return MZ_FALSE;
5925
5926 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, local_dir_header_ofs, local_dir_header,
5927 sizeof(local_dir_header)) != sizeof(local_dir_header))
5928 return MZ_FALSE;
5929
5930 if (!mz_zip_writer_add_to_central_dir(
5931 pZip, pArchive_name, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, NULL, 0, pComment,
5932 comment_size, uncomp_size, comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0,
5933 dos_time, dos_date, local_dir_header_ofs, ext_attributes))
5934 return MZ_FALSE;
5935
5936 pZip->m_total_files++;
5937 pZip->m_archive_size = cur_archive_file_ofs;
5938
5939 return MZ_TRUE;
5940}
5941
5942#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
5943mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_file(mz_zip_archive *pZip, const char *pArchive_name,
5944 const char *pSrc_filename, const void *pComment,
5945 mz_uint16 comment_size, mz_uint level_and_flags,
5946 mz_uint32 ext_attributes) {
5947 mz_uint uncomp_crc32 = MZ_CRC32_INIT, level, num_alignment_padding_bytes;
5948 mz_uint16 method = 0, dos_time = 0, dos_date = 0;
5949 time_t file_modified_time;
5950 mz_uint64 local_dir_header_ofs, cur_archive_file_ofs, uncomp_size = 0,
5951 comp_size = 0;
5952 size_t archive_name_size;
5953 mz_uint8 local_dir_header[MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
5954 MZ_FILE *pSrc_file = NULL;
5955
5956 if ((int)level_and_flags < 0)
5957 level_and_flags = MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL;
5958 level = level_and_flags & 0xF;
5959
5960 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) ||
5961 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING) || (!pArchive_name) ||
5962 ((comment_size) && (!pComment)) || (level > MZ_UBER_COMPRESSION))
5963 return MZ_FALSE;
5964
5965 local_dir_header_ofs = cur_archive_file_ofs = pZip->m_archive_size;
5966
5967 if (level_and_flags & MZ_ZIP_FLAG_COMPRESSED_DATA)
5968 return MZ_FALSE;
5969 if (!mz_zip_writer_validate_archive_name(pArchive_name))
5970 return MZ_FALSE;
5971
5972 archive_name_size = strlen(pArchive_name);
5973 if (archive_name_size > 0xFFFF)
5974 return MZ_FALSE;
5975
5976 num_alignment_padding_bytes =
5977 mz_zip_writer_compute_padding_needed_for_file_alignment(pZip);
5978
5979 // no zip64 support yet
5980 if ((pZip->m_total_files == 0xFFFF) ||
5981 ((pZip->m_archive_size + num_alignment_padding_bytes +
5982 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE +
5983 comment_size + archive_name_size) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
5984 return MZ_FALSE;
5985
5986 memset(&file_modified_time, 0, sizeof(file_modified_time));
5987 if (!mz_zip_get_file_modified_time(pSrc_filename, &file_modified_time))
5988 return MZ_FALSE;
5989 mz_zip_time_t_to_dos_time(file_modified_time, &dos_time, &dos_date);
5990
5991 pSrc_file = MZ_FOPEN(pSrc_filename, "rb");
5992 if (!pSrc_file)
5993 return MZ_FALSE;
5994 MZ_FSEEK64(pSrc_file, 0, SEEK_END);
5995 uncomp_size = MZ_FTELL64(pSrc_file);
5996 MZ_FSEEK64(pSrc_file, 0, SEEK_SET);
5997
5998 if (uncomp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF) {
5999 // No zip64 support yet
6000 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6001 return MZ_FALSE;
6002 }
6003 if (uncomp_size <= 3)
6004 level = 0;
6005
6006 if (!mz_zip_writer_write_zeros(pZip, cur_archive_file_ofs,
6007 num_alignment_padding_bytes +
6008 sizeof(local_dir_header))) {
6009 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6010 return MZ_FALSE;
6011 }
6012 local_dir_header_ofs += num_alignment_padding_bytes;
6013 if (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment) {
6014 MZ_ASSERT((local_dir_header_ofs & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1)) ==
6015 0);
6016 }
6017 cur_archive_file_ofs +=
6018 num_alignment_padding_bytes + sizeof(local_dir_header);
6019
6020 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(local_dir_header);
6021 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_archive_file_ofs, pArchive_name,
6022 archive_name_size) != archive_name_size) {
6023 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6024 return MZ_FALSE;
6025 }
6026 cur_archive_file_ofs += archive_name_size;
6027
6028 if (uncomp_size) {
6029 mz_uint64 uncomp_remaining = uncomp_size;
6030 void *pRead_buf =
6031 pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE);
6032 if (!pRead_buf) {
6033 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6034 return MZ_FALSE;
6035 }
6036
6037 if (!level) {
6038 while (uncomp_remaining) {
6039 mz_uint n = (mz_uint)MZ_MIN(MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE, uncomp_remaining);
6040 if ((MZ_FREAD(pRead_buf, 1, n, pSrc_file) != n) ||
6041 (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_archive_file_ofs, pRead_buf,
6042 n) != n)) {
6043 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
6044 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6045 return MZ_FALSE;
6046 }
6047 uncomp_crc32 =
6048 (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(uncomp_crc32, (const mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf, n);
6049 uncomp_remaining -= n;
6050 cur_archive_file_ofs += n;
6051 }
6052 comp_size = uncomp_size;
6053 } else {
6054 mz_bool result = MZ_FALSE;
6055 mz_zip_writer_add_state state;
6056 tdefl_compressor *pComp = (tdefl_compressor *)pZip->m_pAlloc(
6057 pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1, sizeof(tdefl_compressor));
6058 if (!pComp) {
6059 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
6060 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6061 return MZ_FALSE;
6062 }
6063
6064 state.m_pZip = pZip;
6065 state.m_cur_archive_file_ofs = cur_archive_file_ofs;
6066 state.m_comp_size = 0;
6067
6068 if (tdefl_init(pComp, mz_zip_writer_add_put_buf_callback, &state,
6069 tdefl_create_comp_flags_from_zip_params(
6070 level, -15, MZ_DEFAULT_STRATEGY)) !=
6071 TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY) {
6072 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
6073 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
6074 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6075 return MZ_FALSE;
6076 }
6077
6078 for (;;) {
6079 size_t in_buf_size =
6080 (mz_uint32)MZ_MIN(uncomp_remaining, MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE);
6081 tdefl_status status;
6082
6083 if (MZ_FREAD(pRead_buf, 1, in_buf_size, pSrc_file) != in_buf_size)
6084 break;
6085
6086 uncomp_crc32 = (mz_uint32)mz_crc32(
6087 uncomp_crc32, (const mz_uint8 *)pRead_buf, in_buf_size);
6088 uncomp_remaining -= in_buf_size;
6089
6090 status = tdefl_compress_buffer(pComp, pRead_buf, in_buf_size,
6091 uncomp_remaining ? TDEFL_NO_FLUSH
6092 : TDEFL_FINISH);
6093 if (status == TDEFL_STATUS_DONE) {
6094 result = MZ_TRUE;
6095 break;
6096 } else if (status != TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY)
6097 break;
6098 }
6099
6100 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
6101
6102 if (!result) {
6103 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
6104 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6105 return MZ_FALSE;
6106 }
6107
6108 comp_size = state.m_comp_size;
6109 cur_archive_file_ofs = state.m_cur_archive_file_ofs;
6110
6111 method = MZ_DEFLATED;
6112 }
6113
6114 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
6115 }
6116
6117 MZ_FCLOSE(pSrc_file);
6118 pSrc_file = NULL;
6119
6120 // no zip64 support yet
6121 if ((comp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF) || (cur_archive_file_ofs > 0xFFFFFFFF))
6122 return MZ_FALSE;
6123
6124 if (!mz_zip_writer_create_local_dir_header(
6125 pZip, local_dir_header, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, 0, uncomp_size,
6126 comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0, dos_time, dos_date))
6127 return MZ_FALSE;
6128
6129 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, local_dir_header_ofs, local_dir_header,
6130 sizeof(local_dir_header)) != sizeof(local_dir_header))
6131 return MZ_FALSE;
6132
6133 if (!mz_zip_writer_add_to_central_dir(
6134 pZip, pArchive_name, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, NULL, 0, pComment,
6135 comment_size, uncomp_size, comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0,
6136 dos_time, dos_date, local_dir_header_ofs, ext_attributes))
6137 return MZ_FALSE;
6138
6139 pZip->m_total_files++;
6140 pZip->m_archive_size = cur_archive_file_ofs;
6141
6142 return MZ_TRUE;
6143}
6144#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6145
6146mz_bool mz_zip_writer_add_from_zip_reader(mz_zip_archive *pZip,
6147 mz_zip_archive *pSource_zip,
6148 mz_uint file_index) {
6149 mz_uint n, bit_flags, num_alignment_padding_bytes;
6150 mz_uint64 comp_bytes_remaining, local_dir_header_ofs;
6151 mz_uint64 cur_src_file_ofs, cur_dst_file_ofs;
6152 mz_uint32
6153 local_header_u32[(MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + sizeof(mz_uint32) - 1) /
6154 sizeof(mz_uint32)];
6155 mz_uint8 *pLocal_header = (mz_uint8 *)local_header_u32;
6156 mz_uint8 central_header[MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
6157 size_t orig_central_dir_size;
6158 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
6159 void *pBuf;
6160 const mz_uint8 *pSrc_central_header;
6161
6162 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING))
6163 return MZ_FALSE;
6164 if (NULL ==
6165 (pSrc_central_header = mz_zip_reader_get_cdh(pSource_zip, file_index)))
6166 return MZ_FALSE;
6167 pState = pZip->m_pState;
6168
6169 num_alignment_padding_bytes =
6170 mz_zip_writer_compute_padding_needed_for_file_alignment(pZip);
6171
6172 // no zip64 support yet
6173 if ((pZip->m_total_files == 0xFFFF) ||
6174 ((pZip->m_archive_size + num_alignment_padding_bytes +
6175 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) >
6176 0xFFFFFFFF))
6177 return MZ_FALSE;
6178
6179 cur_src_file_ofs =
6180 MZ_READ_LE32(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_LOCAL_HEADER_OFS);
6181 cur_dst_file_ofs = pZip->m_archive_size;
6182
6183 if (pSource_zip->m_pRead(pSource_zip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_src_file_ofs,
6184 pLocal_header, MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) !=
6185 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
6186 return MZ_FALSE;
6187 if (MZ_READ_LE32(pLocal_header) != MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG)
6188 return MZ_FALSE;
6189 cur_src_file_ofs += MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
6190
6191 if (!mz_zip_writer_write_zeros(pZip, cur_dst_file_ofs,
6192 num_alignment_padding_bytes))
6193 return MZ_FALSE;
6194 cur_dst_file_ofs += num_alignment_padding_bytes;
6195 local_dir_header_ofs = cur_dst_file_ofs;
6196 if (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment) {
6197 MZ_ASSERT((local_dir_header_ofs & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1)) ==
6198 0);
6199 }
6200
6201 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_dst_file_ofs, pLocal_header,
6202 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) !=
6203 MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE)
6204 return MZ_FALSE;
6205 cur_dst_file_ofs += MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;
6206
6207 n = MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
6208 MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS);
6209 comp_bytes_remaining =
6210 n + MZ_READ_LE32(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMPRESSED_SIZE_OFS);
6211
6212 if (NULL ==
6213 (pBuf = pZip->m_pAlloc(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, 1,
6214 (size_t)MZ_MAX(sizeof(mz_uint32) * 4,
6215 MZ_MIN(MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE,
6216 comp_bytes_remaining)))))
6217 return MZ_FALSE;
6218
6219 while (comp_bytes_remaining) {
6220 n = (mz_uint)MZ_MIN(MZ_ZIP_MAX_IO_BUF_SIZE, comp_bytes_remaining);
6221 if (pSource_zip->m_pRead(pSource_zip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_src_file_ofs, pBuf,
6222 n) != n) {
6223 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
6224 return MZ_FALSE;
6225 }
6226 cur_src_file_ofs += n;
6227
6228 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_dst_file_ofs, pBuf, n) != n) {
6229 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
6230 return MZ_FALSE;
6231 }
6232 cur_dst_file_ofs += n;
6233
6234 comp_bytes_remaining -= n;
6235 }
6236
6237 bit_flags = MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_BIT_FLAG_OFS);
6238 if (bit_flags & 8) {
6239 // Copy data descriptor
6240 if (pSource_zip->m_pRead(pSource_zip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_src_file_ofs, pBuf,
6241 sizeof(mz_uint32) * 4) != sizeof(mz_uint32) * 4) {
6242 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
6243 return MZ_FALSE;
6244 }
6245
6246 n = sizeof(mz_uint32) * ((MZ_READ_LE32(pBuf) == 0x08074b50) ? 4 : 3);
6247 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_dst_file_ofs, pBuf, n) != n) {
6248 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
6249 return MZ_FALSE;
6250 }
6251
6252 // cur_src_file_ofs += n;
6253 cur_dst_file_ofs += n;
6254 }
6255 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pBuf);
6256
6257 // no zip64 support yet
6258 if (cur_dst_file_ofs > 0xFFFFFFFF)
6259 return MZ_FALSE;
6260
6261 orig_central_dir_size = pState->m_central_dir.m_size;
6262
6263 memcpy(central_header, pSrc_central_header, MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE);
6264 MZ_WRITE_LE32(central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_LOCAL_HEADER_OFS,
6265 local_dir_header_ofs);
6266 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, central_header,
6267 MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE))
6268 return MZ_FALSE;
6269
6270 n = MZ_READ_LE16(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS) +
6271 MZ_READ_LE16(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS) +
6272 MZ_READ_LE16(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_COMMENT_LEN_OFS);
6273 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(
6274 pZip, &pState->m_central_dir,
6275 pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE, n)) {
6276 mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, orig_central_dir_size,
6277 MZ_FALSE);
6278 return MZ_FALSE;
6279 }
6280
6281 if (pState->m_central_dir.m_size > 0xFFFFFFFF)
6282 return MZ_FALSE;
6283 n = (mz_uint32)orig_central_dir_size;
6284 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets, &n, 1)) {
6285 mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, orig_central_dir_size,
6286 MZ_FALSE);
6287 return MZ_FALSE;
6288 }
6289
6290 pZip->m_total_files++;
6291 pZip->m_archive_size = cur_dst_file_ofs;
6292
6293 return MZ_TRUE;
6294}
6295
6296mz_bool mz_zip_writer_finalize_archive(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
6297 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
6298 mz_uint64 central_dir_ofs, central_dir_size;
6299 mz_uint8 hdr[MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
6300
6301 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING))
6302 return MZ_FALSE;
6303
6304 pState = pZip->m_pState;
6305
6306 // no zip64 support yet
6307 if ((pZip->m_total_files > 0xFFFF) ||
6308 ((pZip->m_archive_size + pState->m_central_dir.m_size +
6309 MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
6310 return MZ_FALSE;
6311
6312 central_dir_ofs = 0;
6313 central_dir_size = 0;
6314 if (pZip->m_total_files) {
6315 // Write central directory
6316 central_dir_ofs = pZip->m_archive_size;
6317 central_dir_size = pState->m_central_dir.m_size;
6318 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = central_dir_ofs;
6319 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, central_dir_ofs,
6320 pState->m_central_dir.m_p,
6321 (size_t)central_dir_size) != central_dir_size)
6322 return MZ_FALSE;
6323 pZip->m_archive_size += central_dir_size;
6324 }
6325
6326 // Write end of central directory record
6327 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(hdr);
6328 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_SIG_OFS,
6329 MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG);
6330 MZ_WRITE_LE16(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_NUM_ENTRIES_ON_DISK_OFS,
6331 pZip->m_total_files);
6332 MZ_WRITE_LE16(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_TOTAL_ENTRIES_OFS, pZip->m_total_files);
6333 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_SIZE_OFS, central_dir_size);
6334 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_OFS_OFS, central_dir_ofs);
6335
6336 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, pZip->m_archive_size, hdr,
6337 sizeof(hdr)) != sizeof(hdr))
6338 return MZ_FALSE;
6339#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6340 if ((pState->m_pFile) && (MZ_FFLUSH(pState->m_pFile) == EOF))
6341 return MZ_FALSE;
6342#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6343
6344 pZip->m_archive_size += sizeof(hdr);
6345
6346 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING_HAS_BEEN_FINALIZED;
6347 return MZ_TRUE;
6348}
6349
6350mz_bool mz_zip_writer_finalize_heap_archive(mz_zip_archive *pZip, void **pBuf,
6351 size_t *pSize) {
6352 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pBuf) || (!pSize))
6353 return MZ_FALSE;
6354 if (pZip->m_pWrite != mz_zip_heap_write_func)
6355 return MZ_FALSE;
6356 if (!mz_zip_writer_finalize_archive(pZip))
6357 return MZ_FALSE;
6358
6359 *pBuf = pZip->m_pState->m_pMem;
6360 *pSize = pZip->m_pState->m_mem_size;
6361 pZip->m_pState->m_pMem = NULL;
6362 pZip->m_pState->m_mem_size = pZip->m_pState->m_mem_capacity = 0;
6363 return MZ_TRUE;
6364}
6365
6366mz_bool mz_zip_writer_end(mz_zip_archive *pZip) {
6367 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
6368 mz_bool status = MZ_TRUE;
6369 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pZip->m_pAlloc) || (!pZip->m_pFree) ||
6370 ((pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING) &&
6371 (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING_HAS_BEEN_FINALIZED)))
6372 return MZ_FALSE;
6373
6374 pState = pZip->m_pState;
6375 pZip->m_pState = NULL;
6376 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir);
6377 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets);
6378 mz_zip_array_clear(pZip, &pState->m_sorted_central_dir_offsets);
6379
6380#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6381 if (pState->m_pFile) {
6382 MZ_FCLOSE(pState->m_pFile);
6383 pState->m_pFile = NULL;
6384 }
6385#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6386
6387 if ((pZip->m_pWrite == mz_zip_heap_write_func) && (pState->m_pMem)) {
6388 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pState->m_pMem);
6389 pState->m_pMem = NULL;
6390 }
6391
6392 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pState);
6393 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_INVALID;
6394 return status;
6395}
6396
6397#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
6398mz_bool mz_zip_add_mem_to_archive_file_in_place(
6399 const char *pZip_filename, const char *pArchive_name, const void *pBuf,
6400 size_t buf_size, const void *pComment, mz_uint16 comment_size,
6401 mz_uint level_and_flags) {
6402 mz_bool status, created_new_archive = MZ_FALSE;
6403 mz_zip_archive zip_archive;
6404 struct MZ_FILE_STAT_STRUCT file_stat;
6405 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(zip_archive);
6406 if ((int)level_and_flags < 0)
6407 level_and_flags = MZ_DEFAULT_LEVEL;
6408 if ((!pZip_filename) || (!pArchive_name) || ((buf_size) && (!pBuf)) ||
6409 ((comment_size) && (!pComment)) ||
6410 ((level_and_flags & 0xF) > MZ_UBER_COMPRESSION))
6411 return MZ_FALSE;
6412 if (!mz_zip_writer_validate_archive_name(pArchive_name))
6413 return MZ_FALSE;
6414 if (MZ_FILE_STAT(pZip_filename, &file_stat) != 0) {
6415 // Create a new archive.
6416 if (!mz_zip_writer_init_file(&zip_archive, pZip_filename, 0))
6417 return MZ_FALSE;
6418 created_new_archive = MZ_TRUE;
6419 } else {
6420 // Append to an existing archive.
6421 if (!mz_zip_reader_init_file(&zip_archive, pZip_filename,
6422 level_and_flags |
6423 MZ_ZIP_FLAG_DO_NOT_SORT_CENTRAL_DIRECTORY))
6424 return MZ_FALSE;
6425 if (!mz_zip_writer_init_from_reader(&zip_archive, pZip_filename)) {
6426 mz_zip_reader_end(&zip_archive);
6427 return MZ_FALSE;
6428 }
6429 }
6430 status =
6431 mz_zip_writer_add_mem_ex(&zip_archive, pArchive_name, pBuf, buf_size,
6432 pComment, comment_size, level_and_flags, 0, 0);
6433 // Always finalize, even if adding failed for some reason, so we have a valid
6434 // central directory. (This may not always succeed, but we can try.)
6435 if (!mz_zip_writer_finalize_archive(&zip_archive))
6436 status = MZ_FALSE;
6437 if (!mz_zip_writer_end(&zip_archive))
6438 status = MZ_FALSE;
6439 if ((!status) && (created_new_archive)) {
6440 // It's a new archive and something went wrong, so just delete it.
6441 int ignoredStatus = MZ_DELETE_FILE(pZip_filename);
6442 (void)ignoredStatus;
6443 }
6444 return status;
6445}
6446
6447void *mz_zip_extract_archive_file_to_heap(const char *pZip_filename,
6448 const char *pArchive_name,
6449 size_t *pSize, mz_uint flags) {
6450 int file_index;
6451 mz_zip_archive zip_archive;
6452 void *p = NULL;
6453
6454 if (pSize)
6455 *pSize = 0;
6456
6457 if ((!pZip_filename) || (!pArchive_name))
6458 return NULL;
6459
6460 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(zip_archive);
6461 if (!mz_zip_reader_init_file(&zip_archive, pZip_filename,
6462 flags |
6463 MZ_ZIP_FLAG_DO_NOT_SORT_CENTRAL_DIRECTORY))
6464 return NULL;
6465
6466 if ((file_index = mz_zip_reader_locate_file(&zip_archive, pArchive_name, NULL,
6467 flags)) >= 0)
6468 p = mz_zip_reader_extract_to_heap(&zip_archive, file_index, pSize, flags);
6469
6470 mz_zip_reader_end(&zip_archive);
6471 return p;
6472}
